2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20researching%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-patio-heater%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguide%20to%20the%20best%20patio%20heaters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20also%20discovered%20that%20the%20higher%20the%20Btu%2C%20the%20better%20%E2%80%94%2040%2C000%20Btu%20is%20a%20good%20baseline%2C%20especially%20for%20cold-weather%20entertaining.%20At%2046%2C000%20Btu%2C%20the%20AmazonBasics%20heater%20is%20mighty%20powerful%20and%20meets%20that%20mark.%20I%20hoped%20it%20would%20extend%20outdoor%20socializing%20well%20into%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAssembly%20and%20ease%20of%20use%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AmazonBasics%20patio%20heater%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd37cd79cf1420018d2ebcf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20temperature%20knob%20are%20located%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20heater%20and%20intuitive%20to%20use.%3Cp%3ESteph%20Coelho%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sleek%2C%20stainless%20steel%2C%20dome-top%20patio%20heater%20arrives%20in%20pieces%2C%20so%20some%20assembly%20is%20required.%20As%20the%20not-so-handy%20one%20in%20my%20household%2C%20I%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20my%20husband%20%E2%80%94%20who%20regularly%2C%20eagerly%20volunteers%20to%20assemble%20other%20people's%20IKEA%20furniture.%20Setup%20took%20about%2040%20minutes%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20clear%20and%20easy-to-follow%20instructions.%20None%20of%20the%20pieces%20were%20warped%20or%20difficult%20to%20put%20together%2C%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20assembled%2C%20getting%20the%20patio%20heater%20ready%20to%20heat%20is%20easy.%20Simply%20twist%20and%20lift%20the%20cover%20to%20load%20up%20a%2020-pound%20propane%20tank%20using%20the%20included%20hose%20and%20regulator%2C%20which%20attach%20the%20same%20way%20you'd%20hook%20up%20a%20propane%20tank%20to%20your%20grill.%20A%20single%20propane%20tank%20should%20last%20around%2010%20hours%20in%20a%20heater%20running%20on%20high%20and%20a%20bit%20longer%20if%20run%20on%20lower%20settings.%20We%20popped%20in%20a%20propane%20tank%20(we%20always%20keep%20one%20on%20hand%20just%20in%20case)%20and%20started%20it%20up.%20I%20was%20immediately%20impressed%20with%20the%20device's%20heat%20output.%20I%20instantly%20felt%20warm%20on%20an%20evening%20when%20my%20exposed%20arms%20were%20dotted%20with%20goosebumps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdjusting%20the%20temperature%20is%20easy%2C%20too.%20Although%2C%20I%20do%20have%20to%20stand%20on%20my%20tippy%20toes%20to%20reach%20the%20ignition%20knob%20and%20adjust%20the%20output%20from%20low%20to%20high.%20Bonus%20being%20that%20if%20you%20have%20kids%2C%20they%20definitely%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20knob%20and%20the%20taller%20height%20keeps%20the%20hottest%20part%20of%20the%20heater%20well%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EReview%20of%20the%20AmazonBasics%20Commercial%20Patio%20Heater%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%20patio%20heater%20with%20dome-shape%20top%2C%20trees%20and%20roof%20of%20house%20in%20background%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20patio%20heaters%20in%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd37d2fe00bce00188babd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20powerful%20AmazonBasics%20Commercial%20Patio%20Heater%20blasts%20out%2046%2C000%20British%20thermal%20units%20(Btu)%20of%20heat.%3Cp%3ESteph%20Coelho%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20day%20we%20assembled%20it%2C%20I've%20used%20the%20AmazonBasics%20heater%20consistently%20%E2%80%94%20on%20chilly%20evenings%2C%20during%20socially%20distanced%20outdoor%20dinners%2C%20and%20to%20keep%20warm%20while%20letting%20the%20dogs%20out%20to%20pee.%20More%20recently%2C%20I've%20tested%20its%20limitations%20in%20more%20uncomfortable%2C%20freezing%20conditions.%20Through%20it%20all%2C%20it's%20allowed%20me%20and%20my%20pod%20of%20outdoor%20guests%20to%20keep%20warm%20when%20we'd%20otherwise%20much%20prefer%20to%20be%20inside.%20I've%20used%20the%20heater%20%3Cem%3Ea%20lot.%20%3C%2Fem%3EMostly%20on%20days%20when%20it's%20cold%20enough%20to%20need%20a%20sweater.%20I%20fired%20it%20up%20a%20few%20times%20to%20enjoy%20breakfast%20with%20my%20parents%20on%20days%20with%20no%20sun%20and%20temperatures%20dipping%20below%2050%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20%E2%80%94%20cold%20enough%20to%20need%20a%20jacket.%20Overall%2C%20I've%20spent%20way%20more%20time%20outside%20during%20the%20fall%20months%20than%20I%20have%20in%20any%20other%20year%2C%20and%20it's%20largely%20in%20part%20to%20having%20the%20heater%20on%20hand%20to%20keep%20me%20warm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20the%20heater's%20boundaries%2C%20I%20took%20it%20to%20my%20patio%20table%20on%20a%20day%20when%20snow%20was%20still%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20it%20was%20almost%2032%20degrees%20outside.%20I%20grabbed%20my%20trusty%20digital%20thermometer%2C%20fired%20up%20my%20laptop%2C%20and%20turned%20on%20the%20patio%20heater%2C%20hoping%20it%20would%20warm%20the%20air%20and%20prevent%20me%20from%20freezing%20while%20I%20tried%20to%20get%20work%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2046%2C000%20Btu%20managed%20to%20raise%20the%20surrounding%20ambient%20temperature%20of%20my%20300-square-foot%20deck%20to%20about%2051%20Fahrenheit.%20It's%20a%20significant%20temperature%20difference%20when%20the%20air%20is%20%3Cem%3Ethat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecold.%20It%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20it%20took%20a%20while%20for%20that%20temperature%20increase%20to%20occur%20%E2%80%94%20about%20two%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20deal%3A%20In%20the%20deep%20cold%20of%20winter%2C%20a%20single%20patio%20heater%20won't%20get%20you%20very%20far%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20you're%20sitting%20around%20a%20table.%20During%20this%20chilly%20test%2C%20my%20lower%20half%20was%20the%20coldest%20part%20of%20my%20body%2C%20which%20was%20tucked%20under%20my%20patio%20table.%20I%20could%20definitely%20see%20myself%20sitting%20out%20there%20longer%20with%20a%20jacket%20and%20a%20warm%20meal%20or%20coffee.%20Still%2C%20I'd%20be%20most%20comfortable%20with%20an%20additional%20compact%20heater%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fmr-heater-buddy-heater-review%5C%22%3EMr.%20Buddy%20Patio%20Heater%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20heating%20up%20my%20legs.%20Of%20course%2C%20sitting%20directly%20under%20the%20heater%20makes%20for%20a%20toastier%20experience%20than%20sitting%20across%20the%20table%20from%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20AmazonBasics%20patio%20heater%20is%20an%20excellent%20option%20for%20keeping%20your%20outdoor%20spot%20comfortable%20during%20chilly%20summer%20nights%20and%20cold%20fall%20evenings%2C%20so%20long%20as%20the%20temperature%20doesn't%20dip%20too%20close%20to%20freezing.%20It's%20also%20apparent%20that%20any%20kind%20of%20breeze%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20slight%20one%20%E2%80%94%20has%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20heating%20performance%2C%20especially%20in%20cold%20weather.%20Over%20the%20many%20months%20I%20used%20the%20heater%2C%20I%20noticed%20I%20always%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20on%20a%20still%20day%20rather%20than%20a%20breezy%20day%2C%20even%20if%20the%20temperatures%20outside%20were%20the%20same.%20Additionally%2C%20you'll%20also%20feel%20warmer%20on%20a%20sunny%20day%20versus%20one%20that's%20overcast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDurability%20and%20storage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%20patio%20heater%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd37db39cf1420018d2ebd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELike%20many%20of%20the%20patio%20heaters%20I've%20researched%20and%20tested%2C%20it's%20big%20but%20still%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20keep%20on%20my%20deck%20all%20year%20long.%3Cp%3ESteph%20Coelho%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heater%20has%20so%20far%20survived%20multiple%20rainstorms%2C%20one%20snowfall%2C%20a%20freeze%2C%20and%20windy%20weather.%20You%20can%20add%20sandbags%20to%20the%20bottom%20for%20added%20sturdiness%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20bother%20and%20it%20never%20once%20wobbled%20on%20stormy%20evenings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20need%20to%20disassemble%20it%20to%20store%20it%20for%20the%20winter.%20You%20can%20keep%20it%20on%20your%20deck%20or%20patio.%20I%20did%20buy%20a%20cover%20for%20it%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20yet%20put%20it%20on%20because%20I%20am%20too%20short%20to%20reach%20on%20my%20own.%20I%20also%20love%20that%20it%20has%20wheels%2C%20and%20you%20can%20roll%20it%20around.%20It's%20easy%20to%20move%20it%20out%20of%20the%20way%20when%20not%20in%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESafety%20features%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AmazonBasics%20heater%20has%20a%20tip-over%20shutoff%20feature%2C%20which%20automatically%20turns%20the%20heater%20off%20if%20it%20falls%20over%20%E2%80%94%20I%20tested%20this%20by%20tipping%20it%20over%20while%20lit%2C%20and%20it%20works%20(I%20don't%20recommend%20trying%20this%20at%20home%2C%20however).%20Despite%20its%20safety%20features%2C%20it's%20always%20important%20to%20be%20vigilant%20around%20any%20heating%20appliances.%20These%20flaming%20patio%20accessories%20can%20warm%20you%20up%20nicely%2C%20but%20they%20can%20also%20do%20some%20damage%20if%20not%20used%20correctly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Griffith%2C%20Prevention%20Section%20Chief%20with%20the%20Montreal%20Fire%20Department%2C%20cautions%20people%20to%20keep%20patio%20heaters%20away%20from%20flammable%20materials%2C%20paying%20attention%20to%20low-hanging%20tree%20branches%2C%20umbrellas%2C%20wooden%20fences%2C%20and%20other%20obstacles.%20He%20also%20warns%20people%20never%20to%20use%20propane-powered%20appliances%20like%20patio%20heaters%20indoors%20because%20they%20emit%20carbon%20monoxide%2C%20which%20can%20be%20deadly%20in%20confined%20spaces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20bottom%20line%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AmazonBasics%20patio%20heater%20is%20now%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20on%20my%20deck.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20how%20much%20use%20I'll%20get%20out%20of%20it%20when%20it's%20regularly%20freezing%20outside%2C%20but%20it%20helped%20me%20extend%20my%20outdoor%20social%20time%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20gathering%20indoors%20felt%20fraught%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20occasionally%20see%20the%20people%20I%20love%20and%20maintain%20safe%20social%20distancing%20%E2%80%94%20even%20just%20for%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20a%20perfect%20solution.%20Ideally%2C%20I'd%20outfit%20my%20patio%20with%20multiple%20heaters%2C%20but%20availability%20and%20cost%20limit%20my%20options.%20The%20heater%20isn't%20capable%20of%20melting%20layers%20of%20snow%2C%20so%20there's%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20moment%20when%20you%20may%20want%20to%20use%20your%20outdoor%20space%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20unusable.%C2%A0%20The%20AmazonBasics%20Outdoor%20Patio%20Heater%20makes%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I've%20conquered%20the%20change%20of%20seasons%20with%20the%20help%20of%20my%20fiery%2C%20warming%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Famazonbasics-patio-heater-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707341798000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd380e5e00bce00188babdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Famazonbasics-patio-heater-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AmazonBasics%20patio%20heater%20is%20a%20sturdy%20outdoor%20heater%20that%20keeps%20you%20warm%20during%20gatherings%20with%20l