%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20found%20fewer%20crowds%20and%20cheaper%20prices%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20get%20more%20out%20of%20every%20day%20there.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20decorations%20and%20festive%20spirit%20of%20the%20holiday%20season%20also%20added%20something%20special%20to%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20I%20flew%20with%20my%20boyfriend%20to%20meet%20his%20family%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-things-to-ask-partner-before-vacationing-with-them-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20time%20traveling%20together%3C%2Fa%3E%20internationally%2C%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20spend%20five%20days%20in%20Italy%2C%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20from%20his%20family's%20home%20in%20Southern%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-skip-in-italy-arent-worth-it-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EItaly%20is%20swarming%20with%20tourists%20in%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20early%20fall%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20travel%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20when%20it's%20less%20busy%20and%20less%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20train%20ride%20from%20Innsbruck%2C%20Austria%2C%20to%20Verona%20took%20just%20over%20three%20hours.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snow%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Italy%20by%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c39b6343bb77284ba460f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20passed%20snow%2C%20sun%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20trees%20on%20the%20ride.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20was%20fairly%20packed%2C%20but%20we%20found%20seats%20together%20without%20reserving%20them%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20traveled%20through%20snowy%20mountains%20and%20tunnels%2C%20the%20Dolomites%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-do-differently-next-trip-to-italy-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epicturesque%20Italian%20countryside%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Around%205%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20we%20arrived%20at%20the%20Verona%20train%20station%20and%20headed%20out%20into%20the%20dark%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%2020-minute%20walk%20from%20the%20train%20station%20to%20our%20hotel%2C%20where%20we%20passed%20a%20huge%20Christmas%20tree%20and%20bustling%20Christmas%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20accommodations%20were%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20city%20and%20much%20cheaper%20than%20I'd%20expected.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gate%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Verona%2C%20Italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c394407a3d2714887876f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20stayed%20close%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20Verona%20mainstays.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we%20only%20booked%20about%20a%20week%20in%20advance%2C%20we%20found%20a%20small%20hotel%20company%20offering%20apartments%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20city%20for%20just%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20for%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stayed%20in%20a%20studio%20apartment%20with%20a%20small%20balcony%20that%20cost%20us%20just%20under%20%24400%20for%20four%20nights.%20In%20September%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20months%20to%20visit%20Verona%2C%20the%20same%20stay%20costs%20about%20%24850.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20everything%20we%20wanted%20to%20see%20in%20the%20city%20and%20less%20than%20two%20blocks%20from%20the%20city's%20famous%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELater%2C%20we%20wandered%20to%20Piazza%20Erbe%2C%20a%20lovely%20old%20square%20just%20a%20few%20minutes%C3%A2%C2%80%C2%99%20walk%20from%20our%20hotel.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Winter%20market%20in%20Verona%2C%20Italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3945f6fcb546d2d4ceea8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20city's%20atmosphere%20was%20warm%20and%20lively.%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPiazza%20Erbe's%20cobblestone%20streets%20were%20lit%20up%20by%20festive%20light%20displays%2C%20and%20we%20spent%20nearly%20an%20hour%20exploring%20the%20winding%20Christmas%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20archway%20seemed%20to%20lead%20to%20a%20new%20cluster%20of%20stalls%2C%20selling%20cheeses%2C%20meats%2C%20wooden%20crafts%2C%20and%20ornaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20was%20crisp%20but%20not%20unpleasant%2C%20with%20the%20temperature%20hovering%20in%20the%20high%2040s%20Fahrenheit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20had%20no%20solid%20plan%20for%20dinner%20that%20night%2C%20but%20easily%20found%20a%20place%20with%20no%20wait.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dinner%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Verona%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c394e96fcb546d2d4ceed4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20washed%20down%20our%20meal%20with%20red%20wine.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20a%20somewhat%20early%20dinner%20since%20we'd%20skipped%20lunch%2C%20and%20finding%20a%20restaurant%20was%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20one%20other%20group%20was%20at%20the%20eatery%20when%20we%20arrived%2C%20and%20tables%20slowly%20filled%20up%20later%20in%20the%20night.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chef%20was%20cooking%20just%20a%20few%20feet%20from%20our%20table%2C%20and%20they%20checked%20in%20on%20us%20several%20times.%20We%20ordered%20two%20pastas%20and%20a%20rabbit%20with%20polenta%2C%20all%20washed%20down%20with%20a%20local%20red%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20meal%2C%20the%20chef%20even%20sent%20us%20free%20shots%20of%20grappa%20(a%20grape-based%20spirit).%20Everything%20was%20delicious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20spent%20the%20next%20day%20exploring%20Verona%20in%20the%20daylight.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Balcony%20from%20Shakespeare's%20Romeo%20and%20Juliet%20in%20Verona.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c395137a3d27148878773d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20people%20seemed%20content%20to%20just%20look%20at%20the%20house%20from%20the%20outside.%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVerona%20is%20a%20midsize%20Italian%20city%20perhaps%20best%20known%20for%20being%20the%20setting%20of%20William%20Shakespeare's%20%26quot%3BRomeo%20and%20Juliet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20Juliet's%20house%2C%20filled%20with%20artifacts%20and%20art%20from%20the%20play's%20history.%20We%20even%20stepped%20outside%20onto%20Juliet's%20famous%20balcony.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20wait%20to%20get%20inside%20the%20house%20%E2%80%94%20another%20perk%20of%20not%20visiting%20during%20busy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20toured%20all%20four%20of%20the%20city's%20main%20famous%20churches.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Church%20in%20Verona.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3952e7a3d27148878774c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPictured%20here%20is%20the%20Chiesa%20di%20Santa%20Anastasia.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20paid%20a%20few%20euros%20for%20all-day%20entry%20to%20all%20of%20the%20churches%20and%20basilicas%20in%20the%20city%2C%20all%20within%20walking%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20very%20few%20other%20tourists%20around.%20Once%20again%2C%20we%20waited%20in%20no%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20no%20crowds%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20move%20quickly%20between%20all%20the%20sites%20we%C3%A2%C2%80%C2%99d%20wanted%20to%20see.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bridge%20over%20the%20river%20in%20Verona.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c395ea6fcb546d2d4cf040%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalking%20around%20Verona%20was%20a%20breeze.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20the%20day%20exploring%20the%20city%20on%20foot%20and%20we%20didn't%20encounter%20many%20crowds%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerona%20also%20has%20a%20beautiful%20river%2C%20and%20we%20enjoyed%20crossing%20back%20and%20forth%20over%20bridges%20several%20times%20during%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20got%20to%20see%20the%20city%20from%20above%2C%20too.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20the%20river%20in%20Verona.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c396097a3d271488787800%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20didn't%20wait%20long%20for%20the%20funicular.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20few%20euros%2C%20we%20rode%20up%20the%20funicular%20to%20arrive%20on%20the%20top%20of%20a%20mountain%20with%20great%20views%20of%20the%20city%20and%20surrounding%20Italian%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20was%20small%2C%20with%20room%20for%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20people%2C%20but%20we%20only%20had%20to%20wait%20the%20length%20of%20the%20ride%20down%20the%20mountain%2C%20around%20five%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20quickly%20stopped%20back%20in%20our%20hotel%20to%20get%20changed%20and%20headed%20to%20dinner.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sardines%20and%20fried%20polenta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c396247a3d271488787842%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20didn't%20wait%20for%20a%20seat%20at%20Trattoria%20de%20Camillo.%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ate%20at%20a%20restaurant%20called%20Trattoria%20de%20Camillo%2C%20where%20the%20owner%20was%20also%20our%20server.%20Once%20again%2C%20we%20didn't%20wait%20for%20a%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20warmly%20welcomed%20us%20and%20even%20took%20the%20time%20to%20pull%20a%20chair%20over%20to%20our%20table%20to%20explain%20the%20menu%2C%20which%20was%20written%20in%20Italian%20on%20a%20chalkboard%2C%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20suggestions%2C%20opting%20for%20seasonal%20and%20local%20specialties%2C%20like%20sardines%20on%20polenta%20as%20an%20appetizer%20and%20huge%20plates%20of%20pumpkin%20risotto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20we%20headed%20out%20into%20the%20wet%2C%20foggy%20morning%20to%20catch%20our%20train%20to%20Milan.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Duomo%20in%20Milan%2C%20Italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3977a43bb77284ba45ee0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMilan%20was%20beautiful.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20lightly%20raining%20as%20we%20walked%20from%20the%20train%20station%20through%20the%20Indro%20Montanelli%20Gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20we%20got%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-worlds-priciest-retail-streets-2010-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuadrilatero%20della%20moda%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Milan's%20famous%20fashion%20district.%20We%20wound%20our%20way%20slowly%20up%20and%20down%20the%20streets%20packed%20with%20designer%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20Galleria%20Vittorio%20Emanuele%20II%2C%20a%20large%2C%20semi-outdoor%20shopping%20mall%20with%20high%2C%20beautiful%20ceilings%20next%20to%20the%20Duomo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20also%20saw%20the%20Duomo%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20once%20again%2C%20we%20didn't%20wait%20long%20to%20do%20so.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stained%20glass%20panel%20in%20the%20Duomo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3981b43bb77284ba45f1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Duomo%20has%20amazing%20stained-glass%20windows.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20bought%20tickets%20at%20the%20door%20of%20the%20Duomo%2C%20where%20there%20was%20a%20short%2C%20quickly-moving%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20part%20was%20the%20stained%20glass%20windows%20in%20the%20back.%20Each%20panel%2C%20lit%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20sun%2C%20showed%20a%20scene%20from%20the%20Bible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20our%20fill%20of%20the%20Duomo%2C%20we%20stepped%20back%20outside%20into%20Milan's%20bustling%20streets%2C%20exploring%20the%20winter%20markets%20surrounding%20the%20famous%20cathedral.%20Finally%2C%20we%20headed%20to%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELunch%20was%20traditional%20Roman%20food.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spaghetti%20in%20Milan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c398786fcb546d2d4cf13b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pasta%20was%20excellent.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20enjoyed%20huge%20balls%20of%20mozzarella%2C%20fried%20artichokes%2C%20and%20big%20plates%20of%20saucy%20al-dente%20pasta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20lunch%2C%20we%20hopped%20on%20an%20underground%20train%20to%20the%20Fondazione%20Prada%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fmoma-musuem-of-modern-art-free-online-coursera-course%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtemporary%20art%20museum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20was%20no%20line%20to%20enter%2C%20and%20in%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20we'd%20seen%20four%20of%20its%20large%20galleries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20we%20woke%20up%20around%208%3A30%20a.m.%20for%20our%20train%20to%20Venice.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boat%20on%20the%20Venice%20Grand%20Canal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c399337a3d2714887879df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20took%20the%20train%20from%20Verona%20to%20Venice.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20from%20Verona%20to%20Venice%20took%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20and%20suddenly%2C%20we%20were%20traveling%20along%20a%20long%20bridge%20surrounded%20on%20both%20sides%20by%20the%20glistening%20Adriatic%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20stop%20in%20Venice%20was%20the%20Vaporetto%2C%20the%20city's%20famous%20water%20bus.%20We%20crowded%20in%20with%20other%20tourists%20and%20local%20Venetians%20to%20explore%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWithin%20the%20first%20few%20stops%2C%20enough%20people%20got%20off%20so%20we%20could%20sit%20near%20the%20front%20of%20the%20boat.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canal%20in%20Venice%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3994743bb77284ba45f6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20wind%20was%20crisp%20and%20the%20view%20was%20spectacular.%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vaporetto%20wasn't%20crowded%20for%20long.%20After%20a%20few%20spots%2C%20we%20moved%20up%20to%20get%20even%20better%20seats.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20traveled%20down%20the%20Grand%20Canal%2C%20Venice's%20main%20throughway%2C%20passing%20under%20bridges%20and%20marveling%20at%20the%20ornate%20buildings%20and%20bustling%20paths%20on%20either%20side%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20the%20next%20few%20hours%20wandering%20Venice's%20tiny%20streets%2C%20canals%2C%20and%20sunny%20plazas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20were%20other%20tourists%20around%2C%20Venice%20never%20felt%20crowded.%20The%20closest%20we%20got%20to%20feeling%20overwhelmed%20was%20when%20we%20suddenly%20found%20ourselves%20surrounded%20by%20a%20throng%20of%20school%20kids%20heading%20home%20for%20lunch%20down%20a%20tiny%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20we%20continued%20walking%2C%20we%20saw%20a%20procession%20of%20boats%2C%20with%20each%20rower%20dressed%20in%20Santa%20hats.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boat%20in%20Venice%2C%20in%20the%20evening%20fog%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c399846fcb546d2d4cf178%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fog%20in%20Venice%20was%20beautiful.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAround%204%20p.m.%2C%20we%20stopped%20at%20a%20small%20caf%C3%83%C2%A9%20by%20the%20water%2C%20for%20Aperol%20spritzes%20and%20an%20afternoon%20cappuccino.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20we%20noticed%20fog%20rolling%20in%2C%20blanketing%20the%20city.%20It%20grew%20noticeably%20quieter%20and%20colder%20within%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20and%20the%20smell%20of%20the%20sea%20grew%20sharper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlthough%20I%20wasn%C3%A2%C2%80%C2%99t%20expecting%20the%20fog%2C%20I%20was%20glad%20we%20got%20to%20see%20it.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fog%20in%20Venice%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c399b343bb77284ba45fed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fog%20in%20Venice%20was%20an%20unexpected%2C%20but%20welcome%20surprise.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFog%20is%20not%20something%20I'd%20ever%20heard%20about%20in%20Venice%2C%20and%20it%20made%20the%20experience%20feel%20more%20special%20and%20unique%2C%20than%20just%20seeing%20the%20famous%20canals%20I'd%20heard%20so%20much%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccurately%20or%20not%2C%20I%20also%20felt%20like%20the%20fog%20and%20darkness%20gave%20me%20more%20insight%20into%20what%20the%20city%20might've%20felt%20like%20centuries%20ago%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20canals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Venice%20didn't%20feel%20as%20touristy%20as%20I'd%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELater%20that%20evening%2C%20we%20headed%20back%20to%20Verona.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arena%20in%20Verona%2C%20Italy%20in%20the%20morning%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c399ea43bb77284ba4600e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20arena%20in%20Verona%20was%20epic%20and%20we%20had%20the%20place%20mostly%20to%20ourselves.%20%3Cp%3EMo%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20our%20last%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-verona-fell-in-love-from-their-balconies-during-lockdown-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eday%20in%20Verona%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20woke%20up%20bright%20and%20early%20to%20squeeze%20in%20a%20quick%20visit%20at%20the%20ancient%20arena%20just%20a%20block%20from%20our%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20some%20of%20the%20first%20visitors%20inside%20and%20enjoyed%20watching%20sunlight%20enter%20the%20arena.%20After%20that%2C%20we%20returned%20to%20the%20train%20to%20leave%20Italy%20and%20continue%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20exploring%20the%20large%20