E%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAncestry%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20in%20recruiting%20for%2027%20years%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20the%20global%20director%20of%20talent%20acquisition%20at%20Ancestry.%20In%20June%2C%20I%20will%20have%20been%20with%20the%20company%20for%20three%20years%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20an%20amazing%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-recruiter-interview-questions-senior-job-candidates-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsible%20for%20global%20talent%20acquisition%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20international%20to%20product%20and%20technology%2C%20two%20very%20large%20organizations%2C%20and%20the%20corporate%20recruiting%20and%20sciences%20side.%20We%20talk%20about%20the%20company's%20direction%20and%20what's%20on%20the%20road%20map%2C%20and%20then%20I%20build%20the%20road%20map%20for%20talent%20acquisition%20according%20to%20where%20the%20company%20is%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20the%20company%20is%20focusing%20on%20is%20diversity.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancestry-deb-liu-dei-global-expansion-diversity-economic-concerns-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20CEO%20has%20doubled%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20her%20efforts%20and%20commitment%20to%20diversifying%20the%20workforce%2C%20ensuring%20everybody%20who%20comes%20through%20has%20an%20equitable%20experience%2C%20but%20recruiting%20diverse%20talent%20comes%20with%20unique%20challenges.%20Our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcareers.ancestry.com%2Fbenefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapproved%20states-to-hire%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20sometimes%20limits%20the%20geographical%20diversity%20we%20can%20tap%20into.%20Despite%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20this%20restriction%20can%20exclude%20potential%20candidates%20who%20could%20bring%20a%20wealth%20of%20diverse%20experiences%20and%20perspectives%20to%20the%20organization%20simply%20because%20of%20their%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20is%20that%20when%20you%20work%20in%20tech%2C%20r%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-benefits-that-attract-tech-workers-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eecruiting%20talent%20from%20tech%20giants%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20bring%20proven%20experience%20but%20may%20also%20narrow%20the%20pipeline%20for%20highly%20skilled%20individuals%20from%20less%20renowned%20organizations.%20This%20often%20means%20missing%20out%20on%20diverse%20talent%20that%20thrives%20outside%20the%20tech-giant%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20pro%20of%20working%20at%20Ancestry%20is%20that%20I%20get%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20brand%20and%20the%20product.%20Here%20are%20three%20tools%20I%20use%20to%20diversify%20our%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Workflow%20software%20for%20recruiting%20and%20operating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20we%20recognized%20within%20six%20months%20of%20me%20being%20here%20was%20that%20our%20applicant-tracking%20system%20wasn't%20necessarily%20jiving%20with%20the%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20using%20Lever%2C%20but%20after%20testing%20and%20looking%20at%20the%20system's%20efficacy%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20implement%20Workday%2C%20a%20recruiting%20software%2C%20to%20have%20a%20more%20seamless%20workflow.%20This%20helped%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-firms-laying-off-employees-again-efficiency-amazon-google-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecruiter%20and%20operational%20efficiency%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Workday%20gives%20us%20transparency%20in%20employee-demographic%20breakdowns%20and%20shows%20us%20how%20our%20diverse%20candidates%20perform%20throughout%20the%20interview%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20metrics%20from%20Workday%20provide%20us%20with%20valuable%20talent%20intelligence%20regarding%20the%20health%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-diversity-inclusion-less-of-an-empty-buzzword-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDEI%20strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20give%20us%20specific%20areas%20to%20zero%20in%20on%2C%20and%20ensure%20talent-delivery%20excellence%20remains%20top%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20CRM%20system%20to%20manage%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20tool%20we%20implemented%20was%20a%20customer-relationship%20management%2C%20or%20CRM%2C%20system.%20Clinch%20is%20our%20CRM%20system%20for%20recruiting%20and%20hosting%20our%20career%20site.%20We%20can%20see%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-companies-need-attract-gen-z-job-seekers-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20where%20talent%20comes%20from%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20use%20that%20from%20a%20sourcing%20perspective.%20Clinch%20helps%20us%20hold%20ourselves%20accountable%20to%20our%20goals%2C%20objectives%2C%20and%20key%20results%20by%20ensuring%20that%20we%20embed%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20in%20our%20recruitment%20metrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20tracking%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20making%20sure%20that%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-diverse-inclusive-workforce-small-business-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalent-acquisition%20efforts%20are%20as%20inclusive%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20are%20strategic%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20a%20workforce%20that%20reflects%20the%20rich%20diversity%20of%20our%20global%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClinch%20also%20tracks%20the%20front%20end%20of%20talent%20attraction%20and%20provides%20important%20data%20on%20how%20Ancestry%20career%20pages%2C%20application%20processes%2C%20and%20employer%20branding%20are%20working.%20Some%20front-end%2