eebot%20X2%20Omni%20Robot%20for%20weeks%20in%20my%201600-square-foot%20home%2C%20which%20consists%20of%20historic%20hardwood%20floors%2C%20laminate%20floors%2C%20and%20two%20large%20rugs.%20Beyond%20testing%2C%20I%20typically%20use%20the%20wet-dry%20robot%20vacuum%20as%20a%20cleaning%20tool%20between%20my%20once-a-week%20deep%20cleaning.%20So%20essentially%2C%20I%20rely%20on%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%20to%20%26quot%3Bclean%20up%26quot%3B%20things%20that%20may%20have%20fallen%20in%20the%20kitchen%20or%20some%20dust%20that%20inevitably%20settles%20in%20the%20study%20because%20I%20live%20in%20a%20historic%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20to%20cover%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20my%20review%20of%20the%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20Robot%20vacuum.%20To%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20you%20to%20understand%20the%20different%20elements%20of%20performance%20and%20technology%20related%20to%20this%20wet-dry%20robot%20vacuum%2C%20I've%20broken%20down%20the%20features%20of%20this%20robot%20into%20different%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20close%20up%20of%20the%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20omni%20on%20the%20base%20and%20its%20onboard%20sensors%20and%20cameras%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a4367a3d271488788074%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20features%20various%20sensors%20and%20onboard%20cameras%20for%20faster%20mapping%2C%20object%20recognition%2C%20and%20more.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20is%20outfitted%20with%20an%20embedded%20laser%20navigation%20system%20known%20as%20dual-laser%20LiDAR%2C%20which%20is%20also%20used%20in%20self-driving%20cars.%20However%2C%20this%20upgraded%20version%20means%20that%20the%20lasers%20are%20built%20into%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20robot%20which%20results%20in%20faster%20mapping%20and%20response%20times%2C%20better%20range%20of%20motion%2C%20and%20more%20cleaning%20accuracy.%20Plus%20with%20True%20Detect%203D%202.0%2C%20the%20robot%20uses%203D%20imaging%20to%20recognize%20objects%20like%20pet%20waste%20or%20a%20phone%20charger%20and%20be%20able%20to%20get%20within%20millimeters%20of%20the%20object%20without%20actually%20touching%20it.%20In%20addition%20to%20being%20able%20to%20recognize%20obstacles%20and%20pets%20up%20to%2032%20feet%20away%20within%20a%20210-degree%20angle%20of%20view%2C%20it%20has%20AI%20machine-learning%20capabilities.%20This%20means%20that%20it%20can%20essentially%20learn%20how%20to%20clean%20your%20home%20better%20and%20get%20closer%20to%20objects%20without%20bumping%20into%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEcovacs%20also%20incorporated%20its%20own%20voice%20assistant%2C%20YIKO%2C%20which%20is%20set%20up%20at%20the%20same%20time%20you%20connect%20the%20robot%20to%20the%20app%2C%20and%20greatly%20helps%20with%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20more%20on%20that%20below.%20It%20can%20recognize%20different%20dialects%20and%20languages.%20With%20YIKO%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20say%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BClean%20living%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20robot%20would%20head%20to%20the%20living%20room%20to%20clean%20it.%20If%20there%20were%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20robot%2C%20as%20it%20got%20caught%20on%20a%20cord%2C%20YIKO%20would%20inform%20me%20of%20the%20issue%20aloud%20(a%20notification%20would%20also%20be%20sent%20to%20my%20phone%20via%20the%20app).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20like%20how%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20is%20thin%20in%20terms%20of%20height%20and%20square%20in%20shape.%20The%20robot%20vacuum%20was%20able%20to%20get%20under%20all%20my%20cabinets%2C%20wardrobes%2C%20beds%2C%20and%20chairs%20with%20ease.%20Most%20robot%20vacuums%20are%20circular%20in%20shape%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20quite%20reach%20corners%20in%20the%20way%20that%20this%20robot%20vacuum%20can.%20In%20fact%2C%20because%20it's%20square%20in%20shape%20and%20has%20an%20edge%20detection%20sensor%2C%20the%20mop%20pads%20can%20get%20within%2030%20mm%20closer%20to%20corners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20Ecovacs%20app%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshots%20from%20the%20Ecovacs%20app%20showing%20the%20basic%20screen%2C%20the%20map%20of%20author's%20house%2C%20and%20various%20cleaning%20settings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a1e77a3d271488787f2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ecovacs%20app%20is%20the%20control%20center%20to%20start%20a%20cleaning%20run%2C%20customize%20settings%2C%20review%20cleaning%20progress%20and%20more.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20had%20downloaded%20the%20Ecovacs%20app%2C%20Mapping%20the%20house%20was%20also%20quicker%20than%20I%20expected.%20The%20robot%20didn't%20have%20to%20move%20over%20a%20spot%20for%20the%20map%20to%20appear.%20Rather%2C%20it%20seemed%20the%20map%20expanded%20when%20the%20robot%20entered%20the%20room%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20was%20accurate%2C%20too.%20The%20map%20can%20appear%20in%202D%20or%203D%20and%20even%20displays%20furniture%20like%20couches.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20divide%20the%20map%20into%20specific%20rooms%2C%20label%20them%20accurately%2C%20and%20even%20provide%20certain%20instructions.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20have%20a%20hallway%20with%20unsealed%20hardwood%20floors%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20any%20water%20touching%20it.%20I%20designated%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bvacuum%20only%26quot%3B%20area%20in%20the%20app.%20It's%20really%20easy%20once%20you%20have%20the%20map%20to%20customize%20the%20vacuum's%20cleaning%20to%20a%20specific%20room%20or%20a%20designated%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20app%2C%20I%20can%20schedule%20when%20I%20want%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20to%20vacuum%20only%2C%20mop%20and%20vacuum%2C%20vacuum%20then%20mop%20or%20mop%20only%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20much%20power%20I%20want%20it%20to%20use%20toward%20vacuuming%20or%20how%20much%20water%20flow%20it%20should%20have%20when%20mopping.%20I%20can%20set%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20scrub%26quot%3B%20mopping%20and%20even%20activate%20its%20vacuum%20power%20when%20it%20detects%20carpet.%20The%20app%20also%20keeps%20track%20of%20a%20cleaning%20log%20and%20shows%20where%20the%20vacuum%20cleaned%20within%20a%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222159%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20the%20video%20manager%20feature%20on%20the%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20showing%20what%20the%20robot%20vacuum%20sess%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a2c27a3d271488787fa2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20video%20manager%20feature%20offers%20a%20view%20of%20what%20the%20X2%20Omni%20%26quot%3Bsees%26quot%3B%20and%20lets%20you%20talk%20to%20others%20in%20the%20room%2C%20as%20well%20as%20manually%20navigate%20the%20robot.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20one%20of%20the%20coolest%20features%20of%20the%20app%20is%20the%20Video%20Manager.%20Once%20you%20enter%20this%20password-protected%20section%20of%20the%20app%2C%20you%20can%20see%20a%20live%20video%20from%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20the%20robot%20vacuum.%20Through%20the%20live%20video%2C%20I%20can%20speak%20to%20whoever%20or%20whatever%20is%20in%20the%20room%20with%20the%20robot%20vacuum%2C%20like%20a%20pet%20or%20a%20partner.%20I%20can%20send%20it%20back%20to%20the%20charging%20station%20or%20even%20tell%20it%20to%20clean%20a%20particular%20part%20of%20the%20house.%20Equally%20as%20exciting%2C%20I%20can%20manually%20guide%20the%20robot%20vacuum%20through%20the%20whole%20house%20with%20a%20controller%20on%20the%20screen.%20There's%20even%20a%20security%20element%20with%20the%20live%20video%20called%20%26quot%3BHome%20Patrol%26quot%3B%20where%20I%20can%20send%20the%20vacuum%20around%20the%20house%20to%20%26quot%3Bpatrol%26quot%3B%20for%20any%20unwanted%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20really%20isn't%20anything%20difficult%20about%20using%20this%20wet-dry%20robot%20vacuum.%20The%20app%20is%20self-explanatory%2C%20and%20the%20settings%20are%20easily%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20thing%20to%20note%20is%20that%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20doesn't%20always%20vacuum%20or%20mop%20in%20a%20gridded%20path.%20It%20appears%20to%20start%20by%20vacuuming%20and%20mopping%20around%20the%20perimeter%20of%20a%20room.%20Sometimes%2C%20it%20cleaned%20in%20an%20up-and-down%20pattern%20throughout%20the%20room%2C%20while%20other%20times%2C%20the%20cleaning%20appeared%20more%20haphazard%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20direction%20it%20took.%20This%20is%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20AI%20integration%20of%20the%20robot%20that%20teaches%20it%20to%20clean%20smarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20robot%2C%20there%20were%20definitely%20the%20occasional%20glitches%2C%20like%20the%20robot%20couldn't%20find%20the%20home%20station%20or%20the%20bumper%20got%20stuck%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20help%20it.%20I've%20tested%20a%20handful%20of%20robot%20products%2C%20be%20they%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20or%20lawnmowers%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20found%20one%20robot%20that%20doesn't%20have%20any%20issues%20at%20all.%20I%20only%20say%20that%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20there%20will%20be%20some%20random%20glitches%20to%20be%20expected%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20diminish%20the%20overall%20capacity%20or%20worth%20of%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20thing%20I'll%20say%20about%20ease%20of%20use%20is%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20robot%20climbing%20over%20thresholds.%20For%20most%20people%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20have%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20climbing%20over%20your%20thresholds.%20Because%20I%20live%20in%20a%20103-year-old%20home%2C%20my%20thresholds%20are%20considerably%20high.%20I'm%20talking%200.5-1%20inches%20tall.%20Surprisingly%2C%20the%20robot%20was%20able%20to%20climb%20over%20all%20but%20one%20threshold%2C%20which%20is%20my%20highest%20threshold.%20Occasionally%2C%20it%20took%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time%20to%20climb%20over%20some%20thresholds%2C%20but%20it%20always%20got%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EVacuuming%20Performance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20ecovacs%20deebot%20x2%20omni%20on%20wood%20floor%20cleaning%20against%20a%20dresser%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a7417a3d27148878833e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20did%20a%20great%20job%20getting%20into%20tight%20spaces%20and%20cleaning%20right%20up%20to%20the%20edges%2C%20as%20well%20as%20maneuvering%20over%20most%20thresholds.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20how%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20Robot%20vacuums.%20In%20particular%2C%20I%20loved%20the%20auto-boost%20suction%20setting%2C%20which%20has%20the%20robot%20automatically%20increase%20suction%20when%20it%20recognizes%20that%20a%20specific%20part%20of%20the%20floor%20is%20dirty%20or%20carpeted.%20The%20vacuum%20has%20the%20capability%20of%20increasing%20suction%20to%208000Pa.%20Within%20the%20app%2C%20users%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20set%20the%20vacuum%20suction%20power%20to%20quiet%2C%20standard%2C%20strong%2C%20or%20max%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20vacuumed%20rugs%20and%20hard%20floors%20equally%20well%20on%20the%20standard%20setting.%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20difference%20between%20the%20two.%20I%20tested%20its%20vacuum%20capability%20by%20sprinkling%20ground%20coffee%2C%20flour%2C%20and%20cereal%20(Cheerio%20shape%2C%20but%20slightly%20larger)%20on%20different%20types%20of%20flooring%20and%20noted%20how%20it%20picked%20up%20hair%20and%20dirt.%20It%20picked%20up%20all%20these%20items%20well%2C%20even%20the%20large%20cereal%2C%20which.%C2%A0%20I%20could%20hear%20the%20robot%20break%20down%20into%20smaller%20pieces%20as%20it%20went%20into%20the%20dustbin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlour%20was%20a%20bit%20fine%20for%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20to%20vacuum%20completely.%20Yes%2C%20it%20picked%20up%20most%20of%20it%2C%20but%20there%20was%20definitely%20some%20residue%20on%20my%20hardwood%20floors%20that%20could%20only%20be%20removed%20with%20the%20robot's%20mopping%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EMopping%20performance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222793%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20x2%20omni%20robot%20vacuum%20mopping%20in%20the%20kitchen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a8176fcb546d2d4cfb99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222095%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BDeep%20Scrubbing%26quot%3B%20mop%20setting%20cleans%20in%20S-shaped%20pattern%20which%20helps%20with%20removing%20stubborn%20stains.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20Robot%20vacuum%20is%20equipped%20with%20two%20circular%20mopping%20pads%20made%20of%20chenille%20fabric.%20When%20in%20use%2C%20the%20robot%20emits%20water%20while%20the%20pads%20quickly%20rotate%20to%20mop%20the%20floor.%20I%20much%20prefer%20robots%20with%20spinning%20mopping%20pads%2C%20such%20as%20this%20one.%20In%20the%20past%20(and%20for%20some%20robot%20vacuums%20now)%2C%20the%20mopping%20pad%20was%20like%20a%20thick%20strip%20of%20fabric%20%E2%80%94%20think%20like%20a%20Swiffer%20pad%20placed%20on%20the%20bottom.%20Such%20mopping%20pads%20picked%20up%20some%20dirt%20and%20grime%20but%20didn't%20provide%20the%20kind%20of%20movement%20needed%20to%20scrub%20a%20spot.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni's%20rotating%20mop%20pads%20are%20a%20better%20mopping%20iteration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mopping%20pads%20did%20a%20good%20job%20of%20picking%20up%20dirt%20and%20grime%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20even%20when%20the%20water%20flow%20was%20set%20on%20low%20or%20medium.%20I%20prefer%20to%20use%20the%20%26quot%3BDeep%20Scrubbing%26quot%3B%20mopping%20setting%20for%20the%20robot%20because%20it%20makes%20the%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20mop%20in%20an%20S-shaped%20pattern%20which%20helps%20with%20removing%20stubborn%20stains.%20That%20said%2C%20there%20were%20times%20when%20the%20robot%20vacuum%20missed%20a%20stain%20in%20its%20movement%20of%20the%20room%20or%20didn't%20have%20enough%20power%20and%20movement%20to%20pull%20up%20tougher%20stains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20bottom%20of%20the%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a7f443bb77284ba4695e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%2C%20including%20the%20high%20speed%20spinning%20mopping%20pads%20made%20of%20chenille%20fabric.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20my%20issue%20with%20the%20mopping%20capability%20of%20the%20robot%20is%20how%20it's%20designed.%20For%20one%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20can%20mop%20as%20well%20as%20a%20regular%20wet-dry%20vacuum.%20It's%20better%20suited%20to%20keep%20your%20floors%20clean%20between%20deep%20cleanings%20with%20a%20handheld%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20or%20regular%20vacuum%20and%20mop.%20I%20say%20this%20because%20the%20mopping%20pads%20might%20pick%20up%20dirt%20and%20grime%2C%20but%20that%20dirt%20and%20grime%20can't%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20pads%20and%20stored%20in%20the%20robot%20itself%20as%20it%20moves%20through%20the%20room.%20Rather%2C%20the%20pads%20continue%20to%20move%20and%20clean%20a%20room%20with%20the%20dirt%20and%20grime%20that%20they%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20previous%20section%2C%20essentially%20moving%20the%20dirt%20and%20grime%20from%20one%20spot%20to%20another.%20(This%20is%20also%20my%20issue%20with%20regular%20mops.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20you%20can%20set%20it%20so%20that%20the%20robot%20returns%20to%20the%20station%20and%20cleans%20the%20pads%20every%2010%20minutes%2C%20but%20we%20still%20have%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20robot%20moving%20dirt%20and%20grime%20within%20a%20space%20for%2010%20minutes%20until%20those%20pads%20are%20cleaned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20should%20point%20out%20is%20that%20the%20mopping%20pads%20automatically%20rise%20up%2015%20mm%20when%20the%20robot%20encounters%20carpet%20or%20passes%20through%20an%20area%20it's%20already%20cleaned.%20This%20is%20a%20nice%20feature%20as%20it%20minimizes%20the%20chance%20that%20dirt%20and%20grime%20are%20put%20down%20in%20clean%20spots.%20However%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20when%20the%20robot%20went%20on%20my%20large%20rugs%2C%20the%20mop%20lift%20wasn't%20so%20high%20that%20it%20didn't%20prevent%20some%20of%20the%20mop%20fibers%20from%20touching%20the%20rugs.%20Now%2C%20it%20didn't%20smear%20dirt%20and%20grime%20on%20the%20rugs%20in%20a%20way%20that%20was%20visible%20to%20me%2C%20but%20I%20could%20tell%20that%20the%20fibers%20were%20slightly%20touching%2C%20so%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20dirt%20and%20grime%20were%20transferred%20to%20the%20rugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECleaning%20and%20maintenance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20top%20lid%20of%20the%20ecovacs%20x2%20omni%20with%20clean%20and%20dirty%20water%20tanks%20and%20instructions%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3a8a143bb77284ba46ace%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaintenance%20instructions%20are%20conveniently%20located%20on%20the%20lid%20for%20easy%20reference%2C%20but%20the%20docking%20station%20fully%20cleans%20and%20dries%20mopping%20pads%20and%20empties%20debris%20following%20a%20cleaning%20run.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20feature%20of%20the%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20Robot%20vacuum%20is%20the%20all-in-one%20cleaning%20station.%20This%20sleek%20black%20cleaning%20station%20hides%20a%20dirty%20water%20tank%2C%20a%20clean%20water%20tank%2C%20and%20a%20dustbin%20bag%2C%20which%20all%20work%20together%20so%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20clean%20the%20robot%20vacuum%20at%20all%20after%20it%20finished%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20station%20is%20designed%20to%20not%20only%20remove%20dust%20and%20debris%20from%20the%20dustbin%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20cleaning%2C%20but%20it%20also%20washes%20the%20mop%20pads%20%E2%80%94%20with%20hot%20water%20if%20you%20so%20designate%20it%20to%20in%20the%20app%20%E2%80%94%20and%20dries%20the%20mop%20pads%20as%20well.%20It%20stores%20dirty%20water%20in%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20until%20it's%20full%20and%20then%20notifies%20you%20to%20empty%20it.%20Essentially%2C%20it's%20a%20hands-off%20self-cleaning%20system.%20When%20the%20dustbin%20is%20emptied%20in%20the%20station%2C%20it%20emits%20a%20sound%20that%20measures%2081%20decibels.%20It%20is%20much%20louder%20than%20the%20noise%20created%20by%20the%20mop%20pads%20being%20washed%20and%20dried%2C%20which%20have%20respective%20ratings%20of%2067%20and%2050%20decibels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20adjust%20some%20cleaning%20settings%20in%20the%20app.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20set%20the%20auto-empty%20frequency%20to%20%26quot%3BSmart%26quot%3B%20mode%2C%20the%20Deebot%20will%20empty%20the%20dustbin%20during%20a%20cleaning.%20This%20is%20a%20good%20option%20for%20those%20with%20pets.%20You%20can%20also%20set%20it%20so%20that%20the%20mop%20pads%20are%20cleaned%20every%2010%2C%2015%2C%20or%2025%20minutes%20and%20washed%20in%20an%20energy-efficient%20mode%2C%20with%20hot%20water%2C%20or%20through%20a%20deep%20washing%20cycle.%20Hot%20air-drying%20time%20can%20also%20be%20adjusted%20to%202%2C3%20or%204%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cutaway%20of%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20Ecovacs%20Omni%20Station%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3d9357a3d27148878b5d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20cutaway%20view%20of%20the%20Omni%20Clean%20station%20shows%20the%20placement%20of%20the%20clean%20and%20dirty%20water%20tanks%20and%20dustbag%2C%20that%20can%20hold%20up%20to%2090%20days%20of%20debris%2C%20or%203%20liters.%3Cp%3EEcovacs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20maintenance%2C%20it'll%20involve%20changing%20the%20dust%20bag%20when%20it's%20full%2C%20refilling%20the%20clean%20water%20tank%2C%20dumping%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%2C%20changing%20the%20filter%20occasionally%2C%20and%20maintaining%20the%20brush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20robot%20vacuums%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20if%20they%20can%20mop%20or%20not%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20your%20expectations%20in%20check.%20As%20much%20as%20robot%20technology%20has%20improved%2C%20I've%20tested%20a%20few%2C%20and%20they%20all%20seem%20to%20experience%20a%20glitch%20on%20occasion.%20Not%20being%20able%20to%20find%20the%20charging%20station%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20common%20error%20for%20robot%20vacuums%2C%20and%20the%20Ecovacs%20Deebot%20X2%20Omni%20Robot%20Vacuum%20suffered%20this%20a%20time%20or%20two.%20Once%2C%20it%20sat%20in%20one%20spot%20spinning%20the%20mopping%20pads%20and%20brush%20and%20didn't%20move%20for%20about%2010%20minutes%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20put%20it%20on%20the%20charging%20station%20for%20a%20reset.%20And%20there%20were%20a%20few%20times%20when%20it%20said%20it%20cleaned%20the%20whole%20house%20but%20had%20only%20cleaned%20two%20rooms.%20These%20glitches%20aren't%20ideal%2C%20but%20they%20happen.%20Perhaps%20with%20more%20updates%2C%20it'll%20occur%20less%20and%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20main%20drawback%20of%20the%20Deebot%20is%20that%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20do%20a%20really%20tough%20mopping%20job%20(I%20don't%20think%20any%20robot%20vacuum%20does).%20The%20rotating%20pads%20will%20clean%20up%20dirt%20and%20grime%2C%20but%20tougher%20stains%20and%20a%20deeper%20clean%20require%20a%20handheld%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20or%20a%20mop%20at%20least%20every%20other%20week.%20This%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20is%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20keep%20the%20house%20tidy%20and%20fairly%20clean%20between%20those%20deep%20clean%20sessions%20and%20want%20to%20do%20that%20completely%20hands-off.%20While%20the%20Deebot%20can%20pick%20up%20the%20mopping%20pads%20when%20it%20goes%20onto%20carpets%20or%20rugs%2C%20it%20couldn't%20lift%20the%20pads%20high%20enough%20not%20to%20touch%20taller%20carpet%20or%20rug%20fibers.%20The%20pads%20slightly%20touched%20my%20rug.%20Now%2C%20if%20the%20mopping%20pads%20were%20cleaned%20before%20they%20touched%20my%20rug%2C%20no%20problem%2C%20but%20if%20they've%20been%20cleaning%20my%20floors%20and%20haven't%20returned%20to%20the%20station%20for%20a%20full%20clean%2C%20then%20some%20dirt%20and%20grime%20could%20get%20on%20my%20rug.%20It's%20hard%20to%20tell%20how%20much%20it%20could%20leave%20behind%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20that%20I%20want%20you%20to%20be%20aware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20other%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-robot-vacuum%5C%22%3E%20wet-dry%20robot%20vacuums%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20consider%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20after%20an%20automated%20cleaning%20station%20with%20limited%20interaction%20on%20your%20part%2C%20expect%20to%20spend%20at%20least%20%241%2C000.%20While%20many%20robot%20vacuums%20have%20auto-debris%20disposal%20docking%20stations%20and%20incorporate%20mopping%20features%2C%20like%20models%20from%20Shark%20and%20iRobot%2C%20few%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20hold%20clean%20and%20dirty%20water%20tanks.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fecovacs-deboot-x1-omni-review%5C%22%3EEcovacs%20Deebot%20X1%20Omni%20Robot%20Vacuum%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20predecessor%20of%20the%20X2%2C%20and%20was%20the%20first%20design%20to%20introduce%20a%20cleaning%20station%20with%20heated%20drying.%20However%2C%20the%20X2%20Omni%20delivers%20stronger%20suction%20and%20more%20intelligent%20navigation%2C%20a%20redesigned%20square%20body%20design%20for%20better%20edge%20cleaning%2C%20a%20slimmer%20docking%20station%2C%20and%20mop%20lifting.%20The%20X1%20Omni%20is%20also%20an%20amazing%20option%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20can%20find%20it%20on%20sale%20since%20it's%20a%20slightly%20older%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D7dfb0ec7be01341b44f799dedcfdab8d0913a764228142519185e21d02d3a6e5%26postID%3D65c390cabf98cb3c6dcdc3ae%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fecovacs-deebot-x2-omni-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Froborock-Vacuum-Auto-Drying-Self-Refilling-Self-Emptying%252Fdp%252FB0CQK9TBNB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoborock%20Q%20Revo%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20several%20hundred%20dollars%20less%20and%20also%20impressed%20us%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20all-in-one%20self-cleaning%20dock%20that%20washes%20and%20dries%20the%20mop%20pads%20and%20an%20app%20that%20offers%20a%202D%20and%203D%20map%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20adjust%20the%20vacuuming%20and%20mopping%20settings.%20The%2