tary%20personnel%20setting%20up%20checkpoints%20at%20some%20places%20in%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts%20amid%20apprehensions%20of%20protests%20by%20the%20tribal%20Gujjar%20and%20Bakkerwal%20communities%20against%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20was%20no%20official%20announcement%20about%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20internet%20service%20in%20the%20two%20districts%2C%20a%20PTI%20report%20quoting%20government%20sources%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprecautionary%20measure%20to%20check%20rumour-mongering%20and%20prevent%20people%20from%20creating%20any%20law%20and%20order%20problem%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGates%20closed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20territory%20administration%20also%20prevented%20the%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20from%20addressing%20a%20party%20rally%20in%20the%20region%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20said%20Imran%20Nabi%20Dar%2C%20a%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20was%20scheduled%20to%20address%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20the%20Sunderbani%20area%20of%20Poonch%20where%20a%20crowd%20of%20about%203000%20party%20workers%20and%20local%20leaders%20had%20gathered%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20party%20source%20said%20that%20both%20the%20main%20gate%20and%20a%20controlled-access%20passage%20to%20Dr%20Farooq%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20residence%20Bhatindi%20locality%20of%20Jammu%2C%20from%20where%20Omar%20was%20scheduled%20to%20leave%20for%20Poonch%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20were%20locked%20from%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20that%20many%20party%20workers%20and%20leaders%20who%20had%20gathered%20at%20Sunderbani%20were%20disappointed%20as%20the%20National%20Conference%20vice-president%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreventing%20political%20parties%20from%20reaching%20out%20to%20their%20workers%20is%20an%20undemocratic%20act%20and%20our%20party%20condemns%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%2C%E2%80%9D%20NC%20spokesperson%20Dar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20gave%20approval%20to%20the%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202023%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20has%20included%20the%20Pahari-speaking%20people%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%2C%20sporadic%20protests%20broke%20out%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20Union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20that%20a%20minor%20protest%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Jammu%20after%20the%20bill%20got%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20nod%20through%20voice%20vote%20on%20Tuesday.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20tribal%20students%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20bill%20and%20tried%20to%20take%20out%20a%20protest%20from%20the%20university%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zahid%20Parwaz%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20tribal%20leader..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoudhary%2C%20who%20is%20the%20state%20president%20of%20Gujjar%20Bakkerwal%20Youth%20Welfare%20Conference%2C%20a%20non-profit%20which%20champions%20the%20cause%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20population%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20authorities%20have%20prevented%20students%20and%20other%20tribals%20from%20raising%20their%20voice%20against%20the%20reservation%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecurity%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20at%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20main%20gate%20to%20prevent%20the%20students%20from%20exercising%20their%20democratic%20rights.%20Some%20of%20us%20were%20detained%20at%20Kothi%20Bagh%20police%20station%20(in%20Srinagar)%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%E2%80%9D%20Choudhary%2C%20who%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20the%20purported%20security%20built-up%20outside%20the%20university%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%20in%20charge%20of%20Jammu%20University%2C%20Professor%20Anju%20Bhasin%2C%20said%20that%20she%20also%20noticed%20the%20security%20forces%20outside%20the%20university%20gate%20when%20she%20came%20to%20her%20office%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20UT%20administration%20may%20have%20done%20it%20to%20preempt%20any%20disturbance.%20Our%20university%20has%20no%20role%20in%20matters%20outside%20the%20campus%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%20amends%20the%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%2C%201989%20to%20create%20separate%20lists%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20for%20Union%20Territories%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20adds%20four%20communities%20to%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20including%20Gadda%20Brahmin%2C%20Koli%2C%20Paddari%20Tribe%2C%20and%20Pahari%20Ethnic%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20house%20also%20passed%20the%20Constitution%20(Scheduled%20Castes)%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20adds%20Valmiki%20community%20as%20a%20synonym%20of%20Chura%2C%20Balmiki%2C%20Bhangi%2C%20and%20Mehtar%20communities%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Rights%20of%20tribals%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20group%20of%20lawyers%20staged%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20bill%20in%20Panama%20Chowk%20locality%20of%20Jammu%20on%20Tuesday.%20A%20video%20from%20the%20protest%20shows%20some%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20personnel%20bundling%20three%20lawyers%20into%20the%20back%20of%20one%20of%20their%20vehicles%20who%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGujjar%20and%20Bakkerwals%20make%20up%20the%20third%20largest%20population%20(of%20J%26amp%3BK)%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20lawyer%20is%20heard%20screaming%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20hit%20the%20streets%20and%20fight%20for%20our%20rights.%20We%20are%20not%20afraid%20of%20their%20tyranny.%20We%20have%20fought%20against%20militancy%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%20We%20have%20kept%20the%20flag%20of%20India%20flying%20high%20but%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20any%20fiddling%20with%20the%20rights%20of%20tribals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinor%20protests%20against%20the%20controversial%20bill%20were%20also%20reported%20from%20the%20summer%20capital%20Srinagar%2C%20and%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%2C%20Pulwama%20and%20Kulgam%20districts%20that%20serve%20as%20the%20temporary%20home%20for%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20who%20traverse%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20during%20the%20summer%20months%20along%20with%20their%20families%20and%20livestock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20groups%20have%20been%20up%20in%20arms%20against%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20of%20granting%20tribal%20status%20to%20the%20culturally-moored%20and%20economically%20privileged%20Paharis%2C%20arguing%20that%20they%20will%20nibble%20away%20at%20the%20jobs%20and%20other%20opportunities%20reserved%20for%20their%20poor%20and%20downtrodden%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVote%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20however%20denied%20the%20charge%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20bill%20was%20one%20of%20the%20several%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cempower%20the%20backward%20and%20downtrodden%E2%80%9D%20sections%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20its%20special%20status%20was%20read%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20NC%E2%80%99s%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%2C%20had%20demanded%20that%20the%20union%20government%20should%20guarantee%20that%20the%20quota%20for%20existing%20STs%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20protected%20following%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20new%20reservation%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20political%20experts%2C%20the%20bill%20is%20part%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20turn%20the%20socially-fragmented%20population%20of%20Paharis%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%20a%20political%20vote%20bank%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20has%20struggled%20to%20make%20inroads%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20been%20wooing%20the%2012%20lakh%20Pahari-speaking%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20who%20can%20influence%20the%20outcome%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20constituencies%20since%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202022%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20a%20packed%20crowd%20in%20Rajouri%20town%20that%20the%20Pahari%20community%20was%20going%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20Act%202019%20provided%20reservation%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20assembly%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707308004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07173820%2F738c0fdb-2245-4405-b5d0-80734653847e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-tribal-paharis-protest-internet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20territory%20administration%20also%20suspended%20internet%20in%20two%20districts%20of%20Pir%20Panjal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-tribal-paharis-protest-internet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20has%20for