22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07151223%2Fimage-1813.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20is%20gathering%20information%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cend%20uses%E2%80%9D%20of%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20(FDI)%20in%20One97%20Communications%2C%20which%20owns%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20(PPB)%2C%20a%20source%20privy%20to%20the%20matter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbanking-finance-fdi-use-in-paytm-under-enforcement-directorate-lens-3386712%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exercise%20is%20to%20ascertain%20if%20the%20foreign%20funds%20were%20used%20for%20investments%20other%20than%20those%20stated%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20FDI%20is%20not%20subject%20to%20rigourous%20end-use%20norms%2C%20but%20foreign%20capital%20raised%20by%20Indian%20companies%20through%20the%20ADR-GDR%20route%20aren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20be%20invested%20in%20real%20estate%20or%20stock%20markets.%20The%20regulations%20are%20principally%20governed%20by%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA)%2C%20%3Cem%3EFE%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20ED%20is%20%E2%80%9Conly%20enquiring%20into%20the%20process%E2%80%9D%20(of%20end-uses%20of%20FDI)%20received%20by%20One97%2C%20while%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20ventured%20into%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinvestigation%E2%80%9D%20into%20the%20matter%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Paytm%20told%20news%20agencies%20that%20allegations%20regarding%20FEMA%20violations%20were%20%E2%80%9Cunfounded%20and%20factually%20incorrect%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters%2C%20CEO%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20and%20other%20Paytm%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance%2Fpaytm-ceo-vijay-shekhar-sharma-officials-meet-rbi-to-discuss-regulatory-concerns-sources%2Farticleshow%2F107448106.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Emet%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20senior%20RBI%20executives%20on%20February%206%20(Tuesday)%20to%20deliberate%20on%20%E2%80%9Ca%20road%20map%20to%20address%20regulatory%20concerns.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Sharma%20also%20met%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20at%20the%20Parliament%20building.%20Sources%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20that%20the%20government%20clarified%20it%20has%20no%20role%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20falls%20within%20the%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%2034%20foreign%20(FDI)%20investors%20hold%20a%20little%20over%2045%25%20in%20One97%20Communications%2C%20and%20over%20450%20FPIs%20together%20have%20a%2018.64%25%20stake%20in%20the%20firm.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20shares%20are%20with%20Sharma%20(9.1%25)%2C%20retail%20investors%20(12.85%25)%2C%20mutual%20funds%20(4.99%25)%2C%20body%20corporates%20(6.33%25)%20and%20others%2C%20the%20newspaper%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20FDI%20rules%2C%2049%25%20FDI%20under%20the%20automatic%20route%20is%20allowed%20in%20the%20private%20banking%20sector%2C%20extendable%20up%20to%2074%25%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20government%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFDI%20in%20fintechs%20are%20governed%20by%20separate%20guidelines%20issued%20by%20the%20RBI%2C%20governing%20electronic%20payments%2C%20know-your-customer%20requirements%20and%20data%20localisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EFE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20ED%20is%20investigating%20another%20aspect%2C%20which%20pertains%20to%20whether%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20has%20facilitated%20any%20transactions%20that%20contributed%20to%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20RBI%20has%20clearly%20prohibited%20PPB%20from%20offshore%20transactions%2C%20but%20if%20the%20platform%20was%20used%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%20then%20it%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20money%20laundering%20was%20the%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EFE.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20pre-registered%20scheduled%20offence%20under%20PMLA%20as%20on%20date%2C%20but%20this%20is%20not%20an%20impediment%20for%20the%20agency%20to%20begin%20a%20probe%20under%20PMLA%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%20has%20directed%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20stop%20allowing%20deposits%20into%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20after%20February%2029%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Frbi-paytm-payment-bank-action%5C%22%3Eciting%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cpersistent%20non-compliances%E2%80%9D.%20The%20services%20barred%20include%20using%20the%20United%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI)%2C%20IMPS%2C%20Aadhaar-enabled%20payments%20and%20bill%20payment%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707303620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07151223%2Fimage-1813.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-gathering-information-on-fdi-use-in-paytm-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20exercise%20is%20to%20ascertain%20if%20the%20foreign%20funds%20were%20used%20for%20investments%20other%20than%20those%20stated%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20the%20'Financial%20Express'%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-gathering-information-on-fdi-use-in-paytm-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain's%20prime%20minister%20defends%20Eurovision%20entry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707302603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fb