ing%20of%20arm%2C%20Darren%20Gough%E2%80%99s%20delivery%20stride%2C%20or%20Dale%20Steyn%E2%80%99s%20impeccable%20release%20%E2%80%93%20kids%20on%20streets%20spend%20years%20mimicking%20this%20to%20perfection%2C%20only%20to%20realise%20the%20impression%20itself%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20do%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20result%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20so%20mediocre%2C%20the%20romanticised%20notion%20immediately%20shatters.%20It%20was%20all%20pretty%20and%20lovely%20in%20their%20imagination.%20But%20you%20were%20not%20really%20your%20heroes.%20Nothing%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20despite%20this%20rather%20crushing%20reality%20check%2C%20the%20obsession%20with%20emulating%20fast%20bowlers%20never%20quite%20wears%20down.%20After%20all%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20visual%20appeal%20of%20the%20art%20that%20makes%20fast%20bowling%20so%20captivating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20comes%20in%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%20The%20Indian%20pace%20spearhead%20operates%20in%20his%20own%20way.%20While%20few%20can%20doubt%20the%20pedigree%2C%20Bumrah%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20graduated%20from%20the%20school%20of%20fast%20bowling%20that%20young%20boys%20on%20the%20streets%20obsess%20over.%20You%20watch%20him%20go%20about%20his%20business%20and%20cannot%20help%20but%20think%20he%20was%20hell-bent%20on%20subverting%20the%20inherent%20charm%20associated%20with%20the%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%E2%80%99s%20action%20can%20be%20described%20as%20the%20perfect%20antidote%20to%20the%20aesthetics%20of%20fast%20bowling.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20being%20quite%20generous.%20At%20no%20point%20in%20his%20run-up%2C%20does%20he%20actually%20run.%20He%20briskly%20walks%2C%20takes%20a%20couple%20of%20jittery%20hops%2C%20opens%20his%20arms%20wide%20and%20almost%20jerks%20the%20ball%20out%20of%20his%20hand%20as%20opposed%20to%20releasing%20it.%20The%20non-bowling%20arm%20points%20to%20the%20first%20slip%20creating%20an%20impossible%20angle%20for%20batsmen%20to%20deal%20with%20where%20everything%20seems%20coming%20in%20to%20them.%20The%20action%20makes%20Bumrah%20a%20practically%20impossible%20bowler%20to%20leave%20no%20matter%20how%20certain%20one%20is%20of%20his%20off-stump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Bumrah%20had%20played%20substantial%20amount%20of%20first-class%20cricket%20before%20making%20his%20Test%20debut%20in%20early%202018%2C%20he%20was%20largely%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20limited-overs%20specialist%20up%20until%20that%20point.%20And%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20no%20reason.%20The%20angle%20that%20he%20so%20much%20relied%20on%20allowed%20him%20to%20relentlessly%20attack%20the%20stumps%20but%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20him%20developing%20a%20ball%20leaving%20the%20right-hander%20%E2%80%93%20a%20skill%20absolutely%20crucial%20for%20a%20bowler%20to%20crack%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07133600%2FF80XQsjWQAAXCfg.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07133600%2FF80XQsjWQAAXCfg.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07133600%2FF80XQsjWQAAXCfg-300x175.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07133600%2FF80XQsjWQAAXCfg-1024x596.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40Jaspritbumrah93%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20could%20bowl%20the%20perfect%20yorker%20wide%20of%20off-stump%2C%20could%20vary%20his%20speeds%20without%20changing%20his%20action%20much%20and%20was%20painfully%20accurate%20with%20his%20lines%20%E2%80%93%20an%20%3Cem%3Eunhittable%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhite-ball%20specimen.%20But%20that%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20the%20ceiling%20of%20his%20prowess.%20Because%20those%20defensive%20skills%2C%20priceless%20as%20they%20may%20be%20in%20shorter%20formats%2C%20are%20hardly%20of%20much%20use%20in%20Tests%20where%20a%20batsman%20isn%E2%80%99t%20actively%20looking%20to%20score%20off%20every%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20six%20years%20since%20that%20debut%20at%20Cape%20Town%20and%20any%20hint%20of%20uncertainty%20over%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20suitability%20to%20play%20Tests%20looks%20incredibly%20na%C3%AFve%20now.%20His%20lengths%20adjust%20seamlessly%20the%20moment%20he%20switches%20between%20formats%2C%20his%20conventional%20swing%20is%20just%20as%20sharp%20as%20anyone%E2%80%99s%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20lethal%20when%20the%20ball%20starts%20to%20reverse%2C%20and%20that%20awkward%20angle%20of%20release%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20point%20of%20difference%20since%20it%20never%20allows%20the%20batters%20to%20leave%20him%20on%20line%20with%20any%20real%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20no%20further%20than%20England%E2%80%99s%20Joe%20Root%20in%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20media%20murmur%2C%20India%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20resorted%20to%20hostile%20pitches%20straightaway%20and%20instead%20showed%20faith%20in%20the%20depth%20of%20their%20bowling%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Root%20walked%20in%20to%20bat%20in%20England%E2%80%99s%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20opening%20Test%20at%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20pitch%20was%20beautifully%20paced%20to%20put%20on%20a%20big%20score.%20But%20a%20sharp%20in-ducker%20from%20Bumrah%20is%20the%20last%20thing%20one%20wants%20to%20face%20at%20the%20start%20of%20his%20innings.%20Root%20was%20beaten%20on%20the%20inside%20edge%20and%20caught%20plumb%20in%20front%20of%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20really%20have%20mattered%20when%20he%20came%20out%20to%20bat%20on%20day%20two%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Vizag.%20The%20pitch%20was%20again%20nicely%20paced%20but%20Rohit%20Sharma%20wasted%20no%20time%20and%20threw%20the%20ball%20to%20Bumrah.%20With%20reverse%20swing%20on%20offer%2C%20Bumrah%20kept%20tempting%20Root%20on%20playing%20at%20one%20outside%20his%20off-stump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoot%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20budge%20easily%20but%20the%20amount%20of%20doubt%20Bumrah%20creates%20in%20a%20batter%E2%80%99s%20head%20becomes%20impossibly%20hard%20to%20negate.%20Root%20let%20two%20go%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKhurdra72916%2Fstatus%2F1753693792014922079%5C%22%3Epoked%20at%20the%20third%20one%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20ball%20that%20breached%20his%20defence%20at%20Hyderabad%20ought%20to%20have%20played%20on%20his%20mind.%20He%20simply%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20allowed%20for%20that%20to%20repeat.%20Well%2C%20he%20succeeded%20at%20that%20but%20only%20to%20edge%20at%20one%20leaving%20him%20and%20furnish%20an%20easiest%20of%20grabs%20to%20the%20first%20slip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20dismissals%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20manufacture%20wickets%20on%20surfaces%20not%20particularly%20conducive%20to%20fast%20bowling.%20But%20Bumrah%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20showboating%20just%20yet.%20What%20followed%20Root%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20at%20Vizag%20is%20hands%20down%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20series%20so%20far%20and%20in%20all%20likelihood%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20topped%20for%20the%20three%20remaining%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOllie%20Pope%2C%20England%E2%80%99s%20fidgety%20middle%20order%20rookie%2C%20never%20quite%20looks%20at%20ease%20in%20the%20middle.%20But%20he%E2%80%99d%20proved%20to%20be%20India%E2%80%99s%20unexpected%20nemesis%20in%20their%20defeat%20in%20the%20first%20Test.%20At%20Vizag%20too%2C%20he%E2%80%99d%20been%20off%20to%20a%20shaky%20start%20and%20was%20just%20about%20surviving%20while%20looking%20like%20getting%20out%20every%20other%20ball.%20Until%20Bumrah%20decided%20to%20end%20his%20struggle%20once%20and%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20things%20in%20cricket%20match%20the%20aesthetics%20of%20a%20reverse%20swinging%20yorker%20of%20surgical%20precision.%20It%20feels%20so%20rewarding%20to%20watch.%20It%E2%80%99s%20reel%20material.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20bowler%20announcing%20he%E2%80%99s%20in%20charge%20and%20that%20the%20batter%20is%20nothing%20more%20than%20an%20expendable%20pawn%20in%20this%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Bumrah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcci.tv%2Fvideo%2F5562004%2Fwatch-on-repeat-jasprit-bumrahs-marvellous-yorker-to-ollie-pope%5C%22%3Etailed%20one%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20to%20Pope%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20say%20any%20of%20those%20things%20aloud%20but%20Pope%20heard%20them%20all.%20Loud%20and%20clear.%20It%20could%E2%80%99ve%20been%20a%20batsman%20of%20much%20higher%20standing%20than%20Pope%E2%80%99s%20and%20it%20still%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20mattered.%20That%20ball%20was%20meant%20for%20a%20higher%20purpose%20than%20merely%20uprooting%20the%20stumps%20and%20earn%20the%20bowling%20team%20advantage.%20It%20was%20to%20remind%20everyone%20watching%20what%20ruthless%2C%20remorseless%2C%20lethal%20fast%20bowling%20looked%20like.%20And%20who%E2%80%99s%20to%20say%20the%20ball%20didn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20its%20purpose%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20549px)%2085vw%2C%20549px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07133717%2FFeM_QiuVsAAB0c6.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07133717%2FFeM_QiuVsAAB0c6.jpeg%20549w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07133717%2FFeM_QiuVsAAB0c6-300x169.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696052%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22309%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40Jaspritbumrah93%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Bumrah%20is%20the%20single%20most%20complete%20fast%20bowler%20of%20his%20generation%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20opinion.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20demonstrable%2C%20definitive%20fact.%20His%20numbers%20pass%20every%20possible%20caveat%20one%20can%20conjure%20up%20and%20but%20for%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20Pat%20Cummins%20%E2%80%93%20another%20generational%20bowler%20%E2%80%93%20nobody%20comes%20close%20to%20him.%20Factor%20in%20his%20ridiculous%20output%20in%20the%20shorter%20formats%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20quite%20possibly%20looking%20at%20a%20bowler%20of%20the%20rarest%20possible%20breed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20being%20the%20easiest%20on%20the%20eye%20has%20deferred%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20elevation%20to%20being%20regarded%20as%20a%20bona%20fide%20legend%20of%20this%20sport.%20It%20takes%20time%20for%20years%20and%20years%20of%20bias%20and%20conditioning%20to%20wear%20off.%20Our%20eyes%20are%20trained%20to%20view%20great%20fast%20bowlers%20a%20certain%20way%20and%20Bumrah%20looks%20like%20none%20of%20those%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdjectives%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejaffa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epeach%3C%2Fem%3E%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20thrown%20as%20leniently%20to%20describe%20his%20deliveries%20as%20they%E2%80%99d%20be%20for%20a%20bowler%20with%20a%20more%20traditional%20action%20who%20looked%20the%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMust%20be%20the%20angle%20the%20batsmen%20struggle%20to%20pick%20for%20the%20time%20being.%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98These%20anomalies%20are%20eventually%20found%20out.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98They%20always%20are.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20of%20time.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20the%20anomaly%20never%20stopped.%20Beating%20the%20batter%20on%20either%20edge%2C%20lifting%20the%20ball%20unusually%20off%20the%20length%2C%20setting%20up%20a%20gorgeously%20deceptive%20slower%20one%2C%20or%20throwing%20in%20the%20sucker-punch%20with%20a%20searing%20yorker%2C%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20repertoire%20sets%20him%20apart%20from%20any%20of%20his%20contemporaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20the%20discipline%20and%20persistence%20to%20repeatedly%20bowl%20into%20the%20channel%20and%20induce%20mistakes%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20possesses%20the%20weapons%20to%20relentlessly%20attack%20when%20he%20wants%20to.%20This%20allows%20him%20to%20minimise%20the%20prize%20of%20the%20tradeoff%20between%20accuracy%20and%20intent.%20He%20takes%20his%20wickets%20conceding%20the%20fewest%20runs%2C%20taking%20fewer%20balls%20than%20most%2C%20and%20manages%20to%20not%20leak%20easy%20runs%20in%20the%20process.%20He%20strikes%20the%20impossible%20balance%20between%20average%2C%20strike%20rate%2C%20and%20economy%20rate.%20Once%20again%2C%20among%20active%20fast%20bowlers%2C%20only%20Pat%20Cummins%20rivals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstats.espncricinfo.com%2Fci%2Fengine%2Fstats%2Findex.html%3Fbowling_pacespin%3D1%3Bclass%3D1%3Bfilter%3Dadvanced%3Borderby%3Dbowling_average%3Bqualmin1%3D100%3Bqualval1%3Dwickets%3Bspanmin1%3D1%2BJan%2B2018%3Bspanval1%3Dspan%3Btemplate%3Dresults%3Btype%3Dbowling%5C%22%3Ethese%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20spent%20nearly%20a%20whole%20year%20away%20from%20cricket%20and%20only%20just%20managed%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20last%20year.%20That%20back%20has%20long%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20kryptonite.%20Former%20greats%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fmy-problem-with-him-michael-holding-reveals-what-makes-jaspit-bumrah-injury-prone%2Fstory-G1brLvqw1cc0VSjtX5C6HI.html%5C%22%3EMichael%20Holding%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fjasprit-bumrah-s-action-isn-t-sustainable-if-i-was-there-i-d-have-told-him-shoaib-akhtar-blames-india-for-mismanagement-101679393639252.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAkhtar%2520suggested%2520that%2520for%2520Bumrah%2Cmatches%2520will%2520prolong%2520his%2520career.%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20expressed%20concern%20over%20his%20action%20that%20they%20think%20forces%20him%20to%20expend%20too%20much%20shoulder%20strength%20to%20generate%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20year-long%20absence%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20out%20of%20order%20to%20wonder%20whether%20he%E2%80%99d%20ever%20return%20the%20same%20bowler%20he%20once%20was.%20Well%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20only%20returned%20a%20better%20bowler.%20It%20of%20course%20reflects%20in%20his%20stats%20but%20a%20bowler%E2%80%99s%20rhythm%20can%20instantly%20be%20told%20from%20how%20the%20ball%E2%80%99s%20coming%20out%20of%20his%20hand.%20And%20ever%20since%20he%E2%80%99s%20returned%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20coming%20out%20beautifully.%20It%20swings%20prodigiously%2C%20his%20tools%20of%20offence%20are%20sharper%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20his%20pace%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20dipped%20one%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20to%20tell%20he%E2%80%99s%20put%20his%20troubled%20back%20behind%20him%20for%20good%20though.%20With%20him%20not%20having%20tweaked%20his%20action%20to%20any%20considerable%20degree%2C%20it%20could%20recur%20any%20time.%20And%20it%20could%20be%20the%20next%20one%20or%20the%20one%20after%20that%20renders%20him%20a%20pale%20shadow%20of%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20he%E2%80%99s%20operating%20at%20the%20level%20he%20is%20currently%2C%20every%20moment%20is%20worth%20savouring%2C%20storing%2C%20recording%20in%20reels%2C%20and%20writing%20verbose%20essays%20such%20as%20this%20one%20about.%20Because%20every%20single%20one%20of%20these%20moments%20is%20incredibly%20satisfying.%20Because%20the%20world%20has%20very%20likely%20not%20seen%20a%20fast%20bowler%20of%20this%20kind%20before.%20India%20most%20certainly%20has%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707301841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F0713