turn%20Great%20Nicobar%20Island%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9CHong%20Kong%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20proposed%20project%2C%C2%A0an%20international%20container%20transhipment%20terminal%2C%20associated%20port%20and%20harbour%20facilities%2C%20airport%2C%20power%20plant%2C%20defence%20base%2C%20industrial%20zones%2C%20as%20well%20as%20major%20urban%20development%20will%20come%20up%20on%20the%20island.%20This%2C%20the%20experts%20say%2C%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20sentence%20for%20the%20Shompen%2C%20tantamount%20to%20the%20international%20crime%20of%20genocide%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20changing%20the%20demography%20and%20allowing%20the%20population%20on%20the%20island%20to%20surge%20by%208%2C000%25%2C%20the%20experts%20say%2C%20the%20proposal%20could%20prove%20detrimental%20to%20the%20Shompen%20people%2C%20who%20have%20lived%20on%20the%20island%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%20largely%20without%20contact%20with%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20the%20complete%20letter%20and%20list%20of%20signatories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDear%20President%20Murmu%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20as%20scholars%20with%20expertise%20on%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide%2C%20are%20writing%20to%20express%20our%20utmost%20concern%20that%20the%20Indigenous%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.survivalinternational.org%2Ftribes%2Fshompen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShompen%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0people%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Great%20Nicobar%20Island%20will%20face%20genocide%20if%20the%20plan%20to%20turn%20their%20island%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9CHong%20Kong%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20goes%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shompen%20people%20have%20lived%20for%20hundreds%20if%20not%20thousands%20of%20years%20in%20harmony%20with%20the%20rich%20natural%20world%20of%20Great%20Nicobar%20Island%2C%20largely%20without%20contact%20with%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20the%20government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20to%20create%20an%20international%20container%20transhipment%20terminal%2C%20associated%20port%20and%20harbour%20facilities%2C%20airport%2C%20power%20plant%2C%20defence%20base%2C%20industrial%20zones%2C%20as%20well%20as%20major%20urban%20development%2C%20proceed%2C%20even%20in%20a%20limited%20form%2C%20we%20believe%20it%20will%20be%20a%20death%20sentence%20for%20the%20Shompen%2C%20tantamount%20to%20the%20international%20crime%20of%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cumulative%20effect%20of%20these%20developments%20and%20the%20proposed%20demographic%20shift%20entailing%20650%2C000%20settlers%2C%20or%20an%208%2C000%25%20increase%20in%20population%2C%20will%20ensure%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20the%20Shompen.%20The%20result%20will%20be%20a%20collective%20psychic%20breakdown%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20devastating%20decline%20in%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20even%20before%20then%2C%20simple%20contact%20between%20the%20Shompen%20%E2%80%93%20who%20have%20little%20to%20no%20immunity%20to%20infectious%20outside%20diseases%20%E2%80%93%20and%20those%20who%20come%20from%20elsewhere%2C%20is%20certain%20to%20result%20in%20a%20precipitous%20population%20collapse.%20The%20mass%20death%20of%20the%20entire%20Shompen%20tribe%20will%20ensue.%20The%20only%20way%20to%20avoid%20the%20obliteration%20of%20the%20Shompen%20is%20for%20the%20project%20to%20be%20abandoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20therefore%2C%20call%20upon%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20all%20relevant%20authorities%2C%20to%20urgently%20cancel%20all%20plans%20for%20the%20Great%20Nicobar%20mega-project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mark%20Levene%2C%20Emeritus%20Fellow%2C%20Parkes%20Centre%20for%20Jewish%2Fnon-Jewish%20Relations%2C%20University%20of%20Southampton%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Raz%20Segal%2C%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20Holocaust%20and%20Genocide%20Studies%20and%20Endow