lled-in-blast-outside-political-partys-office-13062733%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20Secretary-General%20Appoints%20Independent%20Panel%20to%20Examine%20UNRWA's%20Operations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07123556%2FGFp2Hp1WoAA3117.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20has%20appointed%20an%20independent%20panel%20to%20examine%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20(UNRWA)%2C%20in%20response%20to%20allegations%20linking%2012%20UNRWA%20personnel%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNRWA%20has%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20staff%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20was%20set%20up%20in%20consultation%20with%20UNRWA%20Commissioner-General%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%20and%20will%20be%20led%20by%20former%20French%20foreign%20minister%20Catherine%20Colonna%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146207%5C%22%3EUN%20News%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20will%20begin%20working%20from%20February%2014%20and%20an%20interim%20report%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20submitted%20to%20Guterres%20in%20late%20March.%20The%20final%20report%2C%20which%20will%20be%20made%20public%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20late%20April%2C%20according%20to%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Office%20of%20Internal%20Oversight%20Services%20is%20already%20probing%20the%20allegations%20that%2012%20UNRWA%20personnel%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20and%20the%20independent%20panel%E2%80%99s%20probe%20will%20in%20parallel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Israel%20accused%20UNRWA%20staff%20of%20being%20involved%20with%20Hamas%2C%20nine%20Western%20countries%20withdrew%20their%20funding%20for%20the%20agency.%20Given%20the%20scale%20of%20destruction%20in%20Gaza%20due%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20attacks%20which%20it%20claims%20are%20%E2%80%98retaliation%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20and%20which%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20is%20probing%20on%20grounds%20of%20%E2%80%98genocide%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20relief%20work%20has%20been%20viewed%20as%20providing%20essential%20humanitarian%20relief.%20Lazzarini%20had%20said%20this%20funding%20suspension%20is%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20lives%20of%20people%20in%20Gaza%20depends%20on%20this%20support%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channel4.com%2Fnews%2Fisraels-evidence-of-unrwa-hamas-allegations-examined%5C%22%3EChannel%204%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20British%20public%20broadcaster%2C%20has%20raised%20questions%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20dossier%20against%20UNRWA%20personnel%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20just%20six%20pages%20long%20and%20%E2%80%9Cprovides%20no%20evidence%20to%20support%20its%20explosive%20new%20claim%20that%20UNRWA%20staff%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fe326a1d3-7b45-4609-8179-dfb6a66abae9%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Time%3C%2Fem%3Es%3C%2Fa%3E%20too%20raised%20similar%20questions%20in%20a%20report%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20intelligence%20assessment%2C%20which%20has%20been%20seen%20by%20the%20FT%2C%20provides%20no%20evidence%20for%20the%20claims%2C%20which%20it%20says%20are%20based%20on%20smartphone%20intercepts%20and%20captured%20identity%20cards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20accusations%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20UNRWA%2C%20the%20largest%20UN%20organisation%20in%20the%20region%2C%20is%20working%20under%20extremely%20challenging%20conditions%20to%20deliver%20lifesaving%20assistance%20to%20the%20two%20million%20people%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20who%20depend%20on%20it%20for%20their%20survival%20amidst%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20complex%20humanitarian%20crises%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guterres%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20since%20Israel%20had%20made%20these%20accusations%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20cooperation%20would%20be%20required%20during%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNRWA%20has%20been%20highlighting%20the%20scale%20of%20devastation%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20including%20the%20destruction%20of%20its%20own%20health%20centres.%20In%20a%20video%20posted%20to%20X%20recently%2C%20the%20agency%20highlighted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20nothing%20left%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20north%20of%20the%20strip%2C%20UNRWA%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20scale%20of%20destruction%20and%20loss%20is%20staggering%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20north%F0%9F%93%8D%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGazaStrip%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23GazaStrip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20destruction%20and%20loss%20is%20staggering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20footage%20shows%20one%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%20health%20centres.%20There%20is%20nothing%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20unprecedented%20level%20of%20destruction%20and%20forced%20displacement%2C%20taking%20place%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz1el0QfhEe%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fz1el0QfhEe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UNRWA%20(%40UNRWA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%2Fstatus%2F1754530324783239532%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20has%20said%20that%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20wounded%20or%20are%20missing%20in%20Gaza%20since%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20post-October%207%20military%20action%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707292803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07123556%2FGFp2Hp1WoAA3117.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-secretary-general-appoints-independent-panel-to-examine-unrwas-operations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20reports%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20Israel%20has%20not%20provided%20any%20evidence%20linking%20UNRWA%20personnel%20to%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-secretary-general-appoints-independent-panel-to-examine-unrwas-operations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Videocon-ICICI%20Bank%20Loan%20Case%3A%20Bombay%20HC%20Declares%20Arrest%20of%20Chanda%20Kochhar%2C%20Husband%20'Illegal'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07120934%2FEffect-2024-02-07T120925.773.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Bombay%20high%20court%20has%20ruled%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chanda%20Kochhar%2C%20former%20managing%20director%20and%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Deepak%20Kochhar%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20connection%20with%20Videocon%20loan%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Anuja%20Prabhudessai%20and%20Justice%20N.R.%20Borkar%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20February%206%2C%20upheld%20a%20previous%20order%20by%20the%20same%20court%20but%20by%20a%20different%20bench.%20The%20high%20court%20in%20an%20interim%20order%20passed%20in%20January%202023%20had%20granted%20the%20duo%20bail%20soon%20after%20their%20arrest.%20The%20Kochhars%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20in%20December%202022%20in%20what%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20Videocon-ICICI%20Bank%20loan%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20their%20arrest%2C%20they%20moved%20the%20court%20challenging%20their%20arrest%20and%20sought%20it%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D.%20On%20January%209%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20passed%20its%20interim%20order%20which%20not%20only%20granted%20them%20bail%20but%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20CBI%20for%20making%20the%20arrest%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccasual%20and%20mechanical%E2%80%9D%20manner%20without%20application%20of%20mind%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbombay-high-court-says-arrest-of-chanda-kochhar-her-husband-in-icici-bank-videocon-loan-case-illegal%2Fcid%2F1998774%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20Kochhars%2C%20the%20CBI%20had%20also%20arrested%20Videocon%20group%20founder%20Venugopal%20Dhoot%20in%20the%20case.%20He%2C%20too%2C%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20high%20court%20in%20January%202023%20in%20its%20interim%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20the%20Kochhars%20is%20that%20ICICI%20Bank%20had%20sanctioned%20credit%20facilities%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%203%2C250%20crore%20to%20Videocon%20Group%20companies%2C%20promoted%20by%20Dhoot%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Banking%20Regulation%20Act%2C%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20guidelines%2C%20and%20credit%20policy%20of%20the%20private%20sector%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20in%202019%2C%20the%20CBI%20named%20Chanda%20Kochhar%2C%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20and%20Dhoot%20along%20with%20Nupower%20Renewables%20(NRL)%2C%20managed%20by%20Deepak%20Kochhar%2C%20Supreme%20Energy%2C%20Videocon%20International%20Electronics%20Ltd%20and%20Videocon%20Industries%20Ltd%20as%20accused.%20The%20FIR%20was%20filed%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20sections%20related%20to%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20also%20alleged%20that%20in%20an%20act%20of%20%3Cem%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dhoot%20made%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2064%20crore%20in%20Nupower%20Renewables%20through%20Supreme%20Energy%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(SEPL)%2C%20and%20transferred%20SEPL%20to%20Pinnacle%20Energy%20Trust%20managed%20by%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20through%20a%20circuitous%20route%20between%202010%20and%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707291048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07120934%2FEffect-2024-02-07T120925.773.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fvideocon-icici-bank-loan-case-bombay-hc-declares-arrest-of-chanda-kochhar-husband-illegal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Anuja%20Prabhudessai%20and%20Justice%20N.R.%20Borkar%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20February%206%2C%20upheld%20a%20previous%20order%20by%20the%20same%20court%20but%20by%20a%20different%20bench%2C%20granting%20them%20bail%20in%20January%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fvideocon-icici-bank-loan-case-bombay-hc-declares-arrest-of-chanda-kochhar-husband-illegal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22London%20Venue%20Backs%20Out%20of%20Hosting%20LRB%20Lecture%20Series%20Over%20Pankaj%20Mishra's%20Talk%20on%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fpankaj-mishra.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20event%20venue%20in%20London%2C%20Barbican%2C%20has%20reportedly%20backed%20out%20of%20hosting%20a%20series%20of%20lectures%20organised%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ELondon%20Review%20of%20Books%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0because%20of%20a%20planned%20lecture%20by%20author%20Pankaj%20Mishra%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20Holocaust%20and%20allegations%20that%20Israel%20is%20committing%20genocide%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fculture%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F06%2Fbarbican-backs-away-from-hosting-talk-on-alleged-israeli-genocide-in-gaza%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Barbican%20had%20agreed%20to%20host%20the%20event%20until%20LRB%20circulated%20a%20poster%20on%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20talk%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Shoah%20after%20Gaza%E2%80%99%2C%20scheduled%20for%20February%2028.%20The%20description%20of%20the%20talk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lrb.co.uk%2Fpages%2Fstandalone%2Fthe-2024-lrb-winter-lectures-at-saint-james-church-clerkenwell%5C%22%3Estates%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20powerful%20Western%20narrative%20holds%20the%20Shoah%20to%20be%20the%20incomparable%20crime%20of%20the%20modern%20era.%20But%20we%20find%20our%20moral%20and%20political%20consciousness%20profoundly%20altered%20when%20Israel%2C%20a%20country%20founded%20as%20a%20haven%20for%20the%20victims%20of%20genocidal%20racism%2C%20is%20itself%20charged%20with%20genocide.%20What%20is%20the%20fate%20of%20universal%20values%20after%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20collapse%20into%20violent%20nationalism%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarbican%20has%20said%20it%20had%20not%20officially%20finalised%20the%20decision%20to%20host%20the%20series%2C%20and%20LRB%E2%80%99s%20poster%20circulation%20meant%20it%20did%20not%20have%20time%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdo%20the%20careful%20preparation%20needed%20for%20this%20sensitive%20content%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20carefully%20consider%20the%20content%20of%20all%20screenings%2C%20performances%2C%20talks%20and%20exhibitions%20hosted%20by%20the%20Barbican%20before%20agreeing%20to%20host%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELRB%20has%20said%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdisappointed%E2%80%9D%20by%20Barbican%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20disappointed%20that%20the%20Barbican%20withdrew%20from%20hosting%20the%20lectures%20at%20a%20late%20stage%20but%20are%20glad%20that%20this%20important%20series%20is%20going%20ahead%20at%20St%20James%20church%2C%20Clerkenwell%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20an%20LRB%20statement%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%20has%20voiced%20his%20opposition%20to%20Barbican%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20saying%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cbecome%20clear%20that%20war%20crimes%20have%20been%20committed%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20and%20powerful%20people%20who%20have%20supported%20the%20Israeli%20regime%20are%20doubling%20down%20on%20their%20untenable%20position%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20breeds%20a%20pervasive%20sense%20of%20fear%20and%20panic%20that%20infects%20even%20cultural%20institutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20last%20year%2C%20Barbican%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fculture%2F2023%2Fjun%2F21%2Fbarbican-apologises-after-asking-speaker-to-avoid-topic-of-free-palestine%5C%22%3Eforced%20to%20apologise%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20asking%20a%20Palestinian%20speaker%20to%20avoid%20discussing%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20Palestine%E2%80%9D%20during%20an%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707289242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fpankaj-mishra.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flondon-venue-backs-out-of-hosting-lrb-lecture-series-over-pankaj-mishras-talk-on-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Barbican%20had%20agreed%20to%20host%20the%20event%20until%20LRB%20circulated%20a%20poster%20on%20Mishra's%20talk%2C%20titled%20'The%20Shoah%20after%20Gaza'%2C%20scheduled%20for%20February%2028.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flondon-venue-backs-out-of-hosting-lrb-lecture-series-over-pankaj-mishras-talk-on-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Afcon%202023%3A%20Nigeria%20and%20South%20Africa%20ready%20to%20resume%2