%20the%20State%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Flive-in-relationships%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELive-in%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20not%20be%20registered%20in%20cases%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20public%20policy%20and%20morality%26quot%3B%2C%20if%20one%20partner%20is%20married%20or%20in%20another%20relationship%2C%20if%20one%20partner%20is%20a%20minor%2C%20and%20if%20consent%20of%20one%20partner%20was%20obtained%20by%20%26quot%3Bcoercion%2C%20fraud%2C%20or%20misrepresentation%20(with%20regard%20to%20identity)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20told%20NDTV%20a%20website%20is%20being%20prepped%20to%20accept%20details%20of%20live-in%20relationship%2C%20which%20will%20be%20verified%20with%20the%20District%20Registrar%2C%20who%20will%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bsummary%20inquiry%26quot%3B%20to%20establish%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20relationship.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20he%20may%20summon%20either%20or%20both%20partners%2C%20or%20anybody%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20registration%20be%20refused%2C%20the%20Registrar%20must%20inform%20in%20writing%20his%2Fher%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btermination%26quot%3B%20of%20registered%20live-in%20relationships%20requires%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bprescribed%20format%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20invite%20police%20investigation%20if%20the%20Registrar%20feels%20reasons%20for%20the%20relationship%20ending%20are%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%26quot%3B.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20of%20those%20under%2021%20will%20also%20be%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20submit%20live-in%20relationship%20declarations%2C%20or%20providing%20false%20information%2C%20could%20land%20one%20in%20jail%20for%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%20Anyone%20who%20fails%20to%20register%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20will%20face%20a%20maximum%20of%20six%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20be%20fined%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%20Even%20a%20delay%20in%20registration%2C%20by%20as%20little%20as%20a%20month%2C%20will%20trigger%20a%20jail%20term%20of%20up%20to%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20key%20points%20in%20the%20section%20on%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20that%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Assembly%20Tuesday%20morning%20are%20that%20children%20born%20out%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20will%20receive%20legal%20recognition%3B%20i.e.%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Bshall%20be%20a%20legitimate%20child%20of%20the%20couple%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-is-uttarakhands-uniform-civil-code-bill-5002455%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUttarakhand%20Takes%20Up%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3A%20Bill%20Explained%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20the%20same%20official%20told%20NDTV%2C%20means%20%26quot%3Brights%20of%20all%20children%20born%20out%20of%20wedlock%2C%20in%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20or%20via%20incubation%2C%20will%20be%20the%20same...%20no%20child%20can%20be%20defined%20as%20'illegitimate'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20children%20will%20have%20equal%20rights%20in%20inheritance%20(including%20parental%20property)%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20drawing%20attention%20to%20the%20language%20of%20the%20UCC%2C%20which%20refers%20to%20%26quot%3Bchild%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20%26quot%3Bson%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bdaughter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20%26quot%3Bdeserted%20by%20her%20live-in%20partner%26quot%3B%20can%20claim%20maintenance%2C%20the%20UCC%20draft%20also%20said%2C%20although%20it%20does%20not%20specify%20what%20constitutes%20%26quot%3Bdesertion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttarakhand's%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3A%20Explained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20or%20UCC%20refers%20to%20a%20set%20of%20laws%20applicable%20to%20all%20citizens%2C%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20religion%20when%20dealing%20with%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%2C%20and%20adoption%2C%20among%20other%20personal%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20civil%20code%20for%20Uttarakhand%20was%20one%20of%20the%20major%20poll%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20last%20year's%20assembly%20election%2C%20which%20the%20party%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20State-appointed%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20has%20drafted%20a%20749-page%20document%20based%20on%20a%20reported%202.33%20lakh%20pieces%20of%20written%20feedback%20and%20engagement%20with%2060%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20proposals%20include%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20polygamy%20and%20child%20marriage%2C%20a%20standardised%20marriageable%20age%20for%20girls%20across%20all%20faiths%2C%20and%20a%20uniform%20process%20for%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand's%20UCC%20also%20seeks%20to%20ban%20practices%20like%20'%3Cem%3Ehalala%3C%2Fem%3E'%20and%20'%3Cem%3Eiddat%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20which%20are%20the%20Islamic%20practices%20a%20woman%20must%20go%20through%20after%20a%20divorce%20or%20the%20death%20of%20the%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-to-implement-uniform-civil-code-in-2024-tribals-to-be-exempted-chief-minister-himanta-biswa-sarma-4842909%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssam%20To%20Implement%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20In%202024%2C%20Tribals%20Exempt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20isn't%20the%20only%20state%20to%20be%20pushing%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%2C%20with%20Assam%2C%20another%20BJP-ruled%20state%20announcing%20plans%20to%20implement%20similar%20rules%20later%