ing%20Charles%20Diagnosed%20With%20Cancer%2C%20Says%20Buckingham%20Palace%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20at%20the%20moment%20what%20would%20happen%20is%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20like%20Queen%20Camilla%20will%20start%20taking%20in%20some%20of%20the%20events%20scheduled%20for%20the%20King.%20The%20King%20will%20also%20have%20his%20audience%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20which%20he%20has%20every%20Wednesday.%20Queen%20Camilla%20has%20already%20taken%20up%20some%20of%20the%20royal%20duties%20that%20the%20King%20normally%20faces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20King%20Charles%20garnered%20praise%20for%20his%20candidness%20in%20discussing%20a%20prostate%20condition%2C%20prompting%20an%20increased%20awareness%20among%20the%20public%20about%20similar%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20from%20various%20nations%20expressed%20their%20well-wishes%20for%20a%20swift%20recovery%20for%20the%2075-year-old%20King.%20Prime%20Minister%20Sunak%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20and%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20among%20the%20many%20voices%20sending%20messages%20of%20solidarity%20to%20King%20Charles%20and%20the%20British%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20speculation%20about%20the%20line%20of%20succession%2C%20Mr%20Turner%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20King%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20give%20up%20his%20throne%20in%20way%2C%20shape%20or%20form.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20London%2C%20citizens%20expressed%20shock%20and%20sympathy%20at%20the%20news%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis%20for%20anyone%2C%20even%20a%20figure%20as%20prominent%20as%20King%20Charles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707194280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2F9a6oea9o_prince-charles-william-harry-instagram_625x300_23_October_19.jp