ed%20to%20see%20the%20boys%20transporting%20scrap%20materials%20to%20their%20homes%20daily.%20It%20was%20only%20later%20that%20she%20discovered%20they%20were%20constructing%20a%20device%20to%20assist%20farmers%20in%20performing%20multiple%20tasks%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20boys%20were%20in%20Class%206%20when%20the%20pandemic%20started.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20L%26amp%3BT%20started%20providing%20online%20classes%20to%20teach%20science%2C%20arts%20and%20maths.%20The%20students%20were%20given%20easy%20ways%20to%20make%20simple%20projects%20at%20home%2C%20which%20kept%20them%20occupied%20while%20they%20learnt%20the%20important%20concepts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thenmughil%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20despite%20facing%20challenges%20in%20writing%20Tamil%20or%20English%20proficiently%2C%20these%20boys%20exhibit%20a%20remarkable%20understanding%20of%20science%20concepts.%20They%20independently%20constructed%20the%20entire%20device%2C%20delving%20into%20areas%20of%20agriculture%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20their%20adeptness%20in%20practical%20knowledge%20and%20hands-on%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2024%20teams%20(50%20children)%20from%20Chennai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Hazira%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Talegaon%20and%20Mumbai%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20in%20Mumbai%20on%203%20February%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20STEM%20activities%20around%20existing%20curriculums%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20connecting%20with%20underserved%20schools%20without%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20areas%2