dered%20why%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20such%20healthy%20options%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ahana%20began%20running%20and%20opting%20for%20healthier%20food%2C%20she%20noticed%20an%20improvement%20in%20her%20health.%20Reflecting%20on%20her%20childhood%20illnesses%20and%20weight%20issues%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20if%20such%20products%20had%20been%20accessible%20in%20India%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20simpler%20for%20mothers%20like%20hers%20to%20provide%20healthier%20snacks%20to%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20her%20sister-in-law%20in%20India%20was%20facing%20the%20same%20conundrum%20as%20her%20mother%20once%20did%20%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20pack%20nutritious%20food%20for%20her%20daughter%20(who%20has%20Type%201%20diabetes)%20going%20to%20school.%20Two%20generations%20of%20mothers%20were%20facing%20the%20same%20problem%2C%20and%20now%20Ahana%20knew%20what%20her%20business%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20an%20innovation%20hub%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20there%20was%20no%20one%20solving%20the%20problem%20of%20making%20healthier%20biscuits%2C%20cookies%20and%20chips.%20Moms%20still%20had%20to%20give%20their%20children%20maida%20biscuits%20and%20deep-fried%20snacks.%20My%20sister-in-law%20had%20the%20same%20options%20from%20the%20same%20brands%20as%20my%20mother%20did%2C%20almost%2030%20years%20ago!%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20offer%20improved%20products%20to%20families%20and%20working%20professionals%2C%20she%20came%20back%20to%20Mumbai%20in%202018.%20She%20began%20conducting%20surveys%20to%20understand%20people%E2%80%99s%20food%20preferences%20and%20what%20factors%20would%20make%20them%20trust%20a%20new%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20said%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20eat%20healthy%2C%20but%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20compromise%20on%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20now%20Mumbai%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201210px)%20100vw%2C%201210px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221210%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20packing%20Open%20Secret%20products%20at%20their%20factory%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295.jpeg%201210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-300x162.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-500x270.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-768x415.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-150x81.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWomen%20packing%20Open%20Secret%20products%20at%20their%20factory%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20worked%20at%20Procter%20%26amp%3B%20Gamble%20(P%26amp%3BG)%20and%20General%20Mills%2C%20Ahana%20gained%20knowledge%20across%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20consumer%20goods%20industry%2C%20spanning%20supply%20chain%2C%20finance%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20manufacturing.%20In%202019%2C%20she%20left%20General%20Mills%20and%20founded%20Open%20Secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%2C%20the%20second%20director%2C%20provided%20the%20company%20with%20a%20paid-up%20capital%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20Following%20the%20company%20registration%2C%20Ahana%20dedicated%20the%20next%20nine%20months%20to%20crafting%20the%20ideal%20%E2%80%98unjunked%E2%80%99%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20securing%20investment%2C%20her%20initial%20priority%20was%20finding%20a%20suitable%20manufacturing%20facility.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sure%20I%20wanted%20the%20shopfloor%20to%20be%20run%20by%20women.%20When%20I%20looked%20at%20manufacturing%20units%20in%20Bhiwandi%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20there%20was%20a%20big%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20no%20toilets%20for%20women%20as%20there%20were%20only%20men%20in%20all%20these%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20After%20many%20visits%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20her%20own%20factory%20in%20Bhandup%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20would%20be%20operated%20by%20an%20all-women%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20and%20biggest%20challenge%20was%2C%20cracking%20the%20perfect%20recipe%20and%20setting%20up%20an%20assembly%20line%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20the%20first%20challenge%2C%20Ahana%20revisited%20her%20past%20experiences%20at%20other%20companies.%20During%20her%20time%20launching%20new%20products%20for%20a%20previous%20brand%2C%20she%20extensively%20visited%20customers%20in%20metro%20cities%2C%20gaining%20valuable%20insights%20into%20their%20snacking%20preferences.%20Drawing%20on%20this%20knowledge%2C%20she%20conducted%20focus%20groups%20to%20identify%20customer%20favourites%20in%20snacks%2C%20cookies%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20focus%20groups%2C%20we%20asked%20people%20what%20they%20liked%20and%20disliked%20in%20the%20snacks%20they%20were%20eating.%20The%20uniform%20response%20from%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20working%20professionals%2C%20students%20or%20moms%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20maida.%20I%20then%20asked%20them%20what%20they%20found%20healthy%2C%20to%20which%20most%20said%20dry%20fruits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20this%20feedback%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20in-house%20R%26amp%3BD%20team%2C%20Ahana%20worked%20on%20formulating%20the%20perfect%20%E2%80%98unjunked%E2%80%99%20cookie.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20unjunked%20the%20typical%20cookie%20by%20replacing%20maida%20with%2040%20to%2050%20percent%20dry%20fruits%20and%20millet%20using%20less%20sugar.%20Most%20of%20our%20products%20have%20just%201%20to%202%20grams%20of%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20involved%20a%20group%20of%20100%20mothers%2C%20dubbed%20by%20Ahana%20as%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Chief%20Innovation%20Officers%E2%80%99.%20Ahana%20sent%20them%20various%20flavours%20and%20samples%2C%20using%20their%20feedback%20to%20improve%20the%20products.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20helped%20us%20crack%20the%20right%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20asserts%20that%20they%20have%20taken%20measures%20to%20guarantee%20the%20snacks%20remain%20delectable%20even%20after%20substituting%20certain%20ingredients%20with%20their%20nutritious%20counterparts.%20This%20ensures%20that%20customers%20not%20only%20enjoy%20the%20taste%20but%20also%20reap%20health%20benefits%20from%20their%20consumption.%20Hence%2C%20nine%20months%20and%201%2C000%20cookies%20later%2C%20Ahana%20was%20ready%20with%20the%20first%20product%20%E2%80%94%20the%20nutty%20cookie%2C%20which%20to%20date%20is%20their%20bestseller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20challenge%20was%20learning%20how%20to%20manufacture%20the%20product.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20product%20with%20no%20benchmark.%20I%20had%20to%20use%20my%20engineering%20skills%20to%20set%20up%20the%20right%20assembly%20line.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20work%20on%20extending%20the%20shelf%20life%20without%20adding%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20uses%20aluminium%20in%20the%20packaging%20to%20extend%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20her%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20finally%20launched%20%E2%80%98Open%20Secret%E2%80%99%20in%20January%202020%20through%20online%20and%20offline%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981.jpe