%20my%20understanding%20of%20how%20machines%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20operate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20academic%20environment%20provided%20him%20with%20a%20platform%20to%20collaborate%20and%20seek%20assistance.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20college%20offers%20well-equipped%20labs%20and%20professors%20with%20extensive%20knowledge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20three%20years%20of%20research%2C%20Aryan%20successfully%20developed%20the%20first%20prototype%20of%20Agrobot%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20he%20had%20already%20established%20a%20company%20named%20Mera%20Saathi%20Pvt%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAbout%20the%20AgRobot%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Aryan%20had%20a%20vision%20what%20he%20looked%20for%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333997%2Fdiwali-gift-for-maid-government-schemes-for-domestic-workers-to-get-financial-security%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20support.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CI%20reached%20out%20to%20Istart%20%E2%80%94%20a%20flagship%20initiative%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20for%20startups%20in%20Rajasthan%20that%20works%20to%20foster%20innovation%2C%20to%20get%20financial%20help.%20They%20incubated%20me%20and%20I%20got%20a%20place%20to%20work%2C%20labs%20and%20support%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20I%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20government%20via%20Atal%20Innovation%20Mission%20for%20support.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20also%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20from%20my%20college%20in%20terms%20of%20research%20space%20and%20support%20from%20professors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20various%20unique%20features%20of%20his%20robot%2C%20Aryan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20unique%20features%20of%20the%20robot%20is%20that%20it%20can%20analyse%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20condition.%20It%20has%20cameras%20installed%20and%20when%20it%20moves%20on%20the%20field%20it%20can%20analyse%20the%20crop%20in%20real%20time.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20dropper%20on%20the%20top%20which%20helps%20in%20spreading%20the%20seeds%20in%20the%20field%2C%20reducing%20manual%20labour%20for%20the%20farmer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20also%20soil%20moisture%20sensors%20that%20help%20farmers%20to%20analyse%20the%20soil%20and%20look%20for%20any%20pests%20in%20them.%20The%20dropper%20can%20also%20be%20used%20for%20irrigating%20the%20field%20and%20spraying%20pesticides%20if%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20of%20the%20soil%20and%20the%20crop%20is%20done%20using%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20which%20is%20trained%20using%20different%20farming%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20IoT%2C%20we%20have%20made%20the%20robot%20remotely%20controllable.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20use%20the%20robot%20from%20Jaipur%20city%20and%20your%20crops%20are%20in%20Kota%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20log%20in%20to%20the%20application%20that%20I%20have%20developed%20and%20use%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aryan%20won%20the%20Bal%20Shakti%20Award%20for%20his%20innovation.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F