20around%20me%20and%20I%20was%20very%20nervous.%20But%20the%20robot%20garnered%20so%20much%20attention%20that%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20mostly%20farmers%2C%20visited%20my%20stall%20and%20showed%20interest%20in%20my%20work.%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20who%20is%20an%20MLA%20visited%20my%20stall%20and%20congratulated%20me%20on%20my%20innovation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20surreal%20but%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20could%20bring%20such%20an%20innovation%20for%20the%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Aryan%20Singh)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706885858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-4-1706885000.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aryan%20Singh%20from%20Kota%2C%20an%2018-year-old%20recipient%20of%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%2C%20developed%20AgRobot%20%E2%80%94%20an%20AI-powered%20rover%20to%20assist%20farmers%20in%20reducing%20the%20burden%20of%20farm%20labour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340703%2Fkota-student-aryan-singh-invented-ai-powered-agrobot-runs-on-solar-energy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla%20Recalling%20Nearly%202.2%20Million%20Vehicles%20To%20Fix%20Warning%20Lights%20That%20Are%20Too%20Small%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22U.S.%20safety%20regulators%20say%20the%20recall%20will%20be%20done%20with%20an%20online%20software%20update.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706875529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65bcda552300003200807d6d.jpeg%3Fcache%3DN3c1TjNjDK%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftesla-recall_n_65bcd910e4b05c8779f8d7d6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22U.S.%20safety%20regulators%20say%20the%20recall%20will%20be%20done%20with%20an%20online%20software%20update.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftesla-recall_n_65bcd910e4b05c8779f8d7d6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftesla-recall_n_65bcd910e4b05c8779f8d7d6%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftesla-recall_n_65bcd910e4b05c8779f8d7d6%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Couple%20Wins%20Patent%20For%20Biodegradable%20%E2%80%98Leather%E2%80%99%20Made%20From%20Areca%20Palm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20know%20that%2C%20on%20average%2C%20making%20natural%20leather%20results%20in%2017%20kg%20of%20CO2%20emissions%20per%20square%20metre%3F%20This%20means%20that%20each%20bag%20or%20pair%20of%20shoes%20contributes%20to%20the%20release%20of%20several%20kilograms%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F99831%2Fiitb-professor-carbon-emissions-air-pollution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20dioxide%20%3C%2Fa%3Eduring%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20we%20really%20need%20animal%20leather%20luxury%20when%20it%20comes%20at%20such%20an%20environmental%20cost.%20Despite%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20continued%20success%2C%20many%20innovators%20are%20now%20offering%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20alternatives%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308921%2Fpune-entrepreneur-modern-customised-kolhapuris-earn-crores-chappers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20leather.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20these%20innovators%20is%20Suresh%20S%20R%2C%20a%2050-year-old%20areca%20palm%20grower%20from%20Shivamogga%2C%20who%20has%20developed%20a%20100%20percent%20natural%2C%20chemical-free%20vegan%20leather%20made%20out%20of%20areca%20leaves%20and%20husk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20innovative%20and%20good%20for%20the%20environment%20because%20we%20take%20a%20lot%20from%20nature%20and%20give%20back%20nothing.%20So%20I%20thought%20of%20working%20towards%20reducing%20the%20massive%20amount%20of%20carbon%20emission%20caused%20by%20the%20leather%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Bhoomi%20Agri%20Ventures%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Growing%20up%20in%20nature%20motivated%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20was%20born%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Karnataka%20called%20Sringeri.%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20agricultural%20family%2C%20growing%20up%2C%20all%20I%20saw%20around%20me%20was%20nature.%20I%20remember%20running%20around%20in%20the%20farms%20and%20feeling%20blissful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20areca%20palm%20trees%20were%20abundant%20in%20his%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAreca%20plant%20is%20a%20primary%20commercial%20crop%20in%20the%20southern%20districts%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20covering%20more%20than%20one%20lakh%20hectares%20of%20land.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20so%20common%20for%20us%20to%20spot%20them%20growing%20around%20the%20house%20and%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20I%20would%20tear%20its%20leaves%20and%20play%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-1-1706853691.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Footwear%20made%20out%20of%20areca%20palm%20leather.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-1-1706853691.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-1-1706853691-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-1-1706853691-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-1-1706853691-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-1-1706853691-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340588%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFootwear%20made%20out%20of%20areca%20palm%20leather.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20moved%20to%20Shivamogga%20in%201992%20and%20started%20a%20business%20in%201995.%20He%20began%20a%20venture%20dealing%20with%20computer%20sales%20and%20services%2C%20along%20with%20software%20development.%20%E2%80%9COne%20notable%20project%20involved%20creating%20software%20for%20primary%20land%20development%20banks%20across%20Karnataka.%20We%20successfully%20implemented%20the%20software%20in%20around%20100%20branches%2C%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20run%20successfully%20after%2028%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20completing%20many%20years%20in%20the%20business%2C%20he%20yearned%20to%20explore%20new%20pastures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20wanted%20to%20try%20something%20innovative%20and%20nature-friendly%2C%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20where%20to%20look%20for%20inspiration.%20But%20you%20know%20how%20the%20saying%20goes%3B%20you%20find%20good%20things%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20looking!%20Well%2C%20that%20was%20precisely%20what%20happened%20to%20me.%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20how%20people%20were%20making%20fibre-based%20leather%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20deciding%20to%20pursue%20crafting%20vegan%20leather%2C%20he%20started%20searching%20for%20a%20suitable%20plant.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20his%20good%20old%20childhood%20pal%20came%20to%20his%20rescue.%20%E2%80%9CI%20recalled%20how%20areca%20palm%20leaves%20became%20sturdy%20when%20dried%20in%20the%20sun%20and%20soaked%20in%20water.%20I%20knew%20there%20was%20potential%20in%20the%20direction%20I%20was%20heading%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Suresh%20had%20zero%20experience%20in%20the%20field%2C%20he%20started%20looking%20online%20to%20check%20if%20someone%20was%20doing%20something%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20when%20I%20discovered%20Tjeerd%20Veenhoven%2C%20based%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20who%20shared%20similar%20interests.%20We%20collaborated%20to%20bring%20this%20idea%20to%20life%2C%20and%20he%20became%20my%20mentor%20during%20that%20period.%20He%20helped%20me%20understand%20the%20process%20of%20converting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305857%2Fgurugram-duo-quit-job-to-make-leather-alternative-bags-accessories-from-coconut-cactus-waraq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplants%20into%20leather%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20of%20the%20fibre%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPresently%2C%20I%20export%20the%20plant-based%20leather%20I%20produce%20in%20India%20to%20him%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20where%20he%20transforms%20it%20into%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20finally%20in%202020%2C%20Suresh%20co-founded%20Bhoomi%20Agri%20Ventures%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Maithili%2C%20and%20even%20got%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVegan%2C%20chemical-free%20and%20biodegradable%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20informs%20every%20year%2C%20they%20get%20a%20yield%20of%20approximately%204%2C000%20to%204%2C500%20naturally%20shed%20leaves%20from%20a%20single%20hectare.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20cut%20any%20part%20of%20the%20tree%20to%20obtain%20the%20raw%20material%3B%20it%20naturally%20sheds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20the%20fibre%20is%20extracted%20from%20the%20plant%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20harness%20the%20beneficial%20qualities%20of%20areca%20leaves%2C%20which%20have%20two%20types%20of%20fibres.%20We%20extract%20these%20fibres%20and%20also%20utilise%20the%20husk.%20Previously%2C%20people%20would%20discard%20the%20husk%20by%20burning%20it%20in%20gardens%20or%20along%20roadsides.%20I%20thought%2C%20why%20not%20repurpose%20it%20instead%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-2-1706853789.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Suresh%20makes%20products%20such%20as%20diary%20cover%2C%20vanity%20bags%2C%20sandals%2C%20and%20lamp%20made%20out%20of%20the%20vegan%20leather.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-2-1706853789.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-2-1706853789-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-2-1706853789-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-2-1706853789-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-2-1706853789-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340589%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESuresh%20makes%20products%20such%20as%20diary%20covers%2C%20vanity%20bags%2C%20sandals%2C%20and%20lamps%20made%20out%20of%20vegan%20leather.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20extracted%20fibre%20is%20dried%20and%20then%20processed%20to%20make%20vegan%20leather.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20create%20our%20products%20from%20this%20leather%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%20turning%20what%20was%20once%20considered%20waste%20into%20wealth.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20people%20used%20these%20leaves%20as%20firewood%2C%20but%20now%20they%E2%80%99re%20being%20repurposed%20into%20plates%20and%20various%20other%20items%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Suresh%20had%20cracked%20the%20code%20for%20using%20areca%2C%20he%20came%20across%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sheet%20is%20typically%20around%20one%20and%20a%20half%20feet%20in%20length%20and%20one%20and%20a%20half%20feet%20in%20width.%20Due%20to%20this%20size%20limitation%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20create%20many%20things%20from%20a%20single%20sheet.%20The%20sheet%20needed%20to%20be%20elongated%2C%20allowing%20for%20versatile%20use%20across%20various%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20in%20May-June%2C%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20he%20was%20invited%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20invited%20to%20set%20up%20his%20stall%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20right%20beside%20us%20was%20the%20ICR%20Calcutta%20stall.%20They%20mentioned%20having%20a%20specific%20gum%20for%20the%20issue%20we%20were%20facing.%20So%20I%20conducted%20extensive%20research%20on%20fibre%20and%20provided%20them%20with%20all%20the%20necessary%20data%20and%20raw%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20developed%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314893%2Fbengaluru-startup-biodegradable-gud-chewing-gum-helps-cut-plastic-pollution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiodegradable%20gum%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20ICR%20Kolkata%20and%20bought%20the%20rights%20from%20the%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20their%20eco-friendly%20vision%2C%20Suresh%20says%20they%20also%20focus%20on%20uplifting%20marginalised%20communities%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CI%20connect%20with%20the%20SHGs%20in%20and%20around%20Shivamogga%20and%20my%20hometown%20Sringeri%20to%20train%20women%20in%20extracting%20the%20fibre%20and%20sewing%20different%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20been%20working%20with%20four%20Self%20Help%20Groups%20(SHG)%2C%20making%20products%2C%20such%20as%20sandals%2C%20book%20covers%2C%20vanity%20bags%2C%20pen%20stands%2C%20etc%2C%20with%20vegan%20leather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20customer%20base%20is%20spread%20across%20India%20and%20usually%20consists%20of%20businesses%20and%20hotels.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20buyers%20are%20from%20Karnataka%20and%20Maharashtra.%20While%20most%20of%20them%20are%20businesses%2C%20the%20products%20are%20available%20to%20buy%20in%20retail%20and%20through%20our%20website%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED%20S%20Ramesh%2C%20who%20works%20in%20a%20pharma%20company%2C%20says%20he%20was%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20useful%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247050%2Fsustainable-startup-innovation-coconut-water-vegan-leather-eco-friendly-peta-kerala-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20came%20across%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20venture.%20%E2%80%9CTypically%2C%20you%20will%20only%20find%20products%20made%20with%20plastic%20or%20leather%20in%20the%20market.%20But%20when%20I%20found%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20I%20purchased%20pen%20stands%20in%20bulk%2C%20and%20all%20my%20friends%20and%20clients%20loved%20it.%20The%20products%20are%20of%20great%20quality%2C%20durable%2C%20and%20nature-friendly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.