0all%20households%20under%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20we%20never%20knew%20when%20water%20would%20be%20supplied.%20Most%20of%20the%20women%20in%20the%20village%20go%20to%20work.%20On%20days%20when%20water%20is%20supplied%2C%20they%20would%20have%20to%20take%20leave%20or%20not%20be%20able%20to%20fetch%20water.%20Moreover%2C%20houses%20at%20a%20higher%20elevation%20used%20to%20get%20less%20water%20and%20those%20at%20a%20lower%20elevation%20used%20to%20get%20more%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20a%20fixed%20quantity%20of%20water%20is%20being%20supplied%20at%20pre-set%20timings%2C%20irrespective%20of%20elevation.%20Today%2C%20our%20area%20gets%20water%20from%206%20am%20to%208%20am%20every%20day.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303367%2Fbengaluru-women-teach-how-to-compost-grow-vegetables-at-home-using-whatsapp-group-urban-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20created%20in%20which%20water%20supply%20timings%20are%20informed%20to%20us.%20Water%20wastage%20and%20electricity%20bills%20also%20have%20come%20down.%20We%20are%20not%20forced%20to%20take%20leave%20%5Bfrom%20work%5D%20for%20fetching%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalaiselvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20install%20these%20IoT%20devices%20in%20OHTs%20located%20in%20other%20villages%20too.%20%E2%80%9COur%20vision%20is%20to%20harness%20available%20technology%20and%20expand%20this%20initiative%2C%20one%20village%20at%20a%20time%2C%20utilising%20existing%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20DC%20Sunkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ferode.nic.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EErode%20District%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706795664