n-help-visually-impaired-twitter-users-see-pictures-heres%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20visually%20impaired%20%3C%2Fa%3Echild%20has%20different%20needs%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20space%20that%20was%20inclusive%20of%20them%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anand%20Sonecha%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20SEALabs%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20this%20school%20help%20its%20children%20navigate%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20you%20asked!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Found%20inspiration%20in%20many%20place%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20started%20his%20practice%20back%20in%202015%20and%20had%20never%20worked%20on%20developing%20a%20school%20before.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Viren%20Joshi%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20school%2C%20approached%20me%20to%20have%20a%20look%2C%20I%20was%20very%20honoured.%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20get%20to%20the%20school%20and%20start%20the%20designing%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20idea%20behind%20the%20school%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20existing%20building%20but%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20condition.%20It%20was%20a%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20with%20visual%20impairment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20two%20buildings%20%E2%80%94%20one%20was%20a%20hostel%20facility%20and%20the%20other%20one%20was%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20each%20room%2C%20twelve%20to%20fifteen%20students%20were%20living%20in%20bunk%20beds.%20Consequently%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20academic%20building%20and%20convert%20the%20existing%20structure%20entirely%20into%20a%20hostel%20facility.%20This%20would%20allow%20for%20redistribution%20of%20students%20across%20the%20ground%20and%20first%20floors%2C%20while%20providing%20them%20with%20more%20comfortable%20and%20improved%20living%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%