rt%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(You%20can%20watch%20more%20of%20Dhiraj%20Takri%E2%80%99s%20content%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdhirajtakri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Instagram%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dhiraj%20Takri)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706622666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDhiraj-Takri-Instagram-1706621044.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhiraj%20Takri%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20content%20creator%20from%20rural%20Odisha%2C%20has%20become%20an%20internet%20sensation%20for%20teaching%20people%20on%20Instagram%20how%20to%20speak%20English%20like%20an%20American%20by%20incorporating%20snippets%20from%20web%20series%20and%20TV%20shows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%202%20Brothers%20Used%20Tech%20%26amp%3B%20Tradition%20To%20Turn%20Their%20Dad%E2%80%99s%2055-YO%20Mithai%20Shop%20into%20a%20Profitable%20Biz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Harshit%20Agrawal%20was%20all%20of%2010%20years%20old%2C%20his%20favourite%20pastime%20was%20sitting%20at%20his%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F208578%2Fvegan-chocolate-dairy-free-cookies-healthy-cake-options-millet-recipes-order-online-lifestyle-tan42%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Elphinstone%20Road.%20Chubby%20legs%20swinging%20in%20the%20air%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99