%2Fdiwali-2020-how-to-celebrate-green-no-noise-ecofriendly-alternative-seed-crackers-sweets-madhya-pradesh-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20linkages%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20coming%20up%20with%20the%20packaging%20for%20Pistabarfi%2C%20I%20got%20the%20image%20licensed%20from%20Tara%20Books%2C%20and%20they%20were%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20oblige.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harshit%20and%20Tanay%20Agrawal%20have%20retained%20their%20family%20legacy%20of%20mithai%20making%20with%20Pistabarfi%2C%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarshit%20and%20Tanay%20Agrawal%20have%20retained%20their%20family%20legacy%20of%20mithai%20making%20with%20Pistabarfi%2C%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Harshit%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20Pistabarfi%2