iv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20younger%20years%2C%20Rajiv%20has%20been%20creating%20various%20products.%20Amidst%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20he%20constructed%20a%20comfortable%20PPE%20kit%20suitable%20for%20extended%20wear.%20As%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%2C%20he%20also%20developed%20over%2050%20wheelchairs%20for%20injured%20or%20paralysed%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20practised%20carpentry%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20adept%20at%20tools%20and%20electrical%20design%20due%20to%20my%20course%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20found%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20air%20fresheners%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etruly%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20passion%20for%20creation%20pushed%20him%20to%20build%20one%20using%20natural%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20poisonous%20chemicals%20in%20air%20fresheners.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20read%20the%20ingredient%20list%20behind%20any%20air%20freshener.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20safe%20for%20children%20(mentioned%20in%20the%20packaging)%20and%20animals%20to%20inhale.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20freshener%20which%20was%20safe%20for%20the%20environment%20as%20well%20as%20humans%20and%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Rajiv%20focused%20on%20creating%20natural%20fragrances%20using%20flower%20waste.%20He%20collected%20jasmine%20and%20roses%20from%20a%20nearby%20temple%2C%20air-dried%20the%20petals%2C%20ground%20them%20into%20powder%20using%20a%20mixer%2C%20and%20combined%20them%20with%20coconut%20husk%20waste.%20After%20allowing%20the%20mixture%20to%20air%20dry%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%20the%20fragrance%20was%20prepared.%20Rajiv%20then%20placed%20this%20fragrance%20into%20a%20glass%20bottle%20and%20crafted%20an%20outer%20cover%20using%20wood%2C%20resulting%20in%20his%20homemade%2C%20eco-friendly%20fragrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2P9fEGofLa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2P9fEGofLa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2P9fEGofLa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20ALVE%20GREEN%20SOLUTIONS%20(%40alveindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20may%20seem%20straightforward%2C%20creating%20the%20final%20product%20involved%20numerous%20trials%20and%20combinations%20for%20Rajiv.%20With%20support%20from%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20ALVE%20Green%20Solutions%2C%20he%20worked%20diligently%20for%20over%20eight%20months.%20It%20took%20more%20than%2020%20prototypes%20before%20achieving%20the%